quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaaf, Kasam hai quran-e-majeed ki"
  50,2,"Balke in logon ko taajub is baat par hua ke ek khabardar karne wala khud inhi mein se inke paas aa gaya, phir munkireen kehne lagey “yeh to ajeeb baat hai"
  50,3,Kya jab hum mar jayenge aur khaak (mitti) ho jayenge (to dobara uthaye jayenge)? Yeh wapasi to aqal se baeed hai”
  50,4,Zameen inke jism mein se jo kuch khati hai woh sab hamare ilm mein hai aur hamare paas ek kitaab hai jismein sab kuch mehfooz hai
  50,5,Balke in logon ne to jis waqt haqq inke paas aaya usi waqt usey saaf jhutla diya. Isi wajah se ab yeh uljhan mein padey huey hain
  50,6,"Accha, to kya inhon ne kabhi apne upar aasmaan ki taraf nahin dekha? Kis tarah humne usey banaya aur aarasta (zeenat/ beautify) kiya, aur usmein kahin koi rakhna(cracks/rifts) nahin hai"
  50,7,Aur zameen ko humne bichaya aur ismein pahadh jamaye aur uske andar har taraah ki khush manzar nabataat uga di
  50,8,Yeh saari cheezein aankhein kholne wali aur sabaq dene wali hain har us bandey ke liye jo (haqq ki taraf) rujoo karne wala ho
  50,9,"Aur aasmaan se humne barkat wala paani naazil kiya,phir ussey baagh aur fasal ke galley"
  50,10,Aur buland o baala khajoor ke darakht paida kardiye jinpar phalon(fruits) se ladey khoshey teh-bar-teh lagte (fruit arranged in layers) hain
  50,11,Yeh intizaam hai bandon ko rizq dene ka is pani se hum ek murda zameen ko zindagi baksh dete hain (marey huey Insano ka zameen se) nikalne bhi isi tarah hoga
  50,12,"In se pehle Nooh ki qaum, aur ashab-ur-rass ,aur Samood"
  50,13,"Aur Aad, aur Firoun , aur Lut ke bhai"
  50,14,"Aur aykah( dwellers in the wood) wale, aur tubba ki qaum ke log bhi jhutla chuke hain har ek ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya , aur aakhir e kaar meri waeed(threat) un par chaspan ho gayi"
  50,15,Kya pehli baar ki takhleeq(creation) se hum aajiz (worn out) thay? Magar ek nayi takhleeq ki taraf se yeh log shakk mein padey huey hain
  50,16,Humne Insaan ko paida kiya hai aur uske dil mein ubharne wale waswason tak ko hum jaante hain. Hum to us ki rag-e-gardan(jugular vein) se bhi zyada us se qareeb hain
  50,17,(aur hamare is barah-e-raast ilm ke alawa)do kaatib(scribes) uske dayein aur bayein baithay(farishtey) har cheez sabt(likh) kar rahe hain
  50,18,Koi lafz us ki zubaan se nahin nikalta jisey mehfooz karne ke liye ek hazir baash nigraan maujood na ho
  50,19,"Phir dekho, woh maut ki jaan-kani (agony of death) haqq lekar aa pahunchi, yeh wahi cheez hai jisse tu bhaaghta tha"
  50,20,"Aur phir sur (trumpet) phoonka gaya, yeh hai woh din jiska tujhe khauf dilaya jata tha"
  50,21,Har shaks is haal mein aa gaya ke uske saath ek haank(drive) kar lane wala hai aur ek gawahi dene wala
  50,22,"Is cheez ki taraf se tu gaflat mein tha, humne woh purda hata diya jo tere aagey pada hua tha aur aaj teri nigaah khoob tez hai"
  50,23,Uske saathi ne arz kiya ye jo meri supurdgi mein tha haazir hai
  50,24,"Hukum diya gaya “phenk do jahannum mein har katte (hardened, stubborn) kaafir ko jo haqq se inaad rakhta tha"
  50,25,"Khair ko roakne wala aur hadd se tajauz (exceeds the limits) karne wala tha, shakk mein pada hua tha"
  50,26,Aur Allah ke saath kisi dusre ko khuda banaye baitha tha. Daal do usey sakht azaab mein”
  50,27,"Uske saathi ne arz kiya “khuda-wanda, maine isko sarkash nahin banaya balke yeh khud hi parle darje ki gumrahi mein pada hua tha”"
  50,28,"Jawab mein irshad hua “mere huzoor jhagda na karo, main tumko pehle hi anjaam-e-badd se khabardar kar chuka tha"
  50,29,Mere haan (yahan) baat palti nahin jaati aur main apne bandon par zulm todhne wala nahin hoon”
  50,30,Woh din jabke hum jahannum se puchenge kya tu bhar gayi? Aur woh kahegi kya aur kuch hai
  50,31,"Aur Jannat muttaqin ke qareeb le aayi jayegi, kuch bhi dur na hogi"
  50,32,"Irshad hoga “yeh hai woh cheez jiska tumse waada kiya jata tha, har us shaks ke liye jo bahut rujoo karne wala aur badi nigehdaasht (watchful of his conduct) karne wala tha"
  50,33,"Jo bay dekhe Rehman se darta tha, aur jo dil-e-girwida liye huey aaya hai"
  50,34,Dakhil ho jao Jannat mein salamati ke saath” woh din hayat-e-abadi (eternity) ka din hoga
  50,35,"Wahan unke liye woh sab kuch hoga jo woh chahenge, aur hamare paas issey zyada bhi bahut kuch unke liye hai"
  50,36,Hum unse pehle bahut si qaumon ko halaak kar chuke hain jo insey bahut zyada taaqatwar thi aur duniya ke mulkon ko unhon ne chaan maara tha phir kya woh koi jaaye panaah paa sakey
  50,37,"Is tareekh mein ibrat ka sabaq hai har us shaks ke liye jo dil rakhta ho, ya jo tawajju se baat ko suney"
  50,38,Humne zameen aur aasmaano ko aur unke darmiyan ki saari cheezon ko chey(six) dino mein paida kardiya aur humein koi thakaan laahiq na hui
  50,39,"Pas aey Nabi, jo baatein yeh log banate hain unpar sabr karo, aur apne Rubb ki hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karte raho, tulu-e-aftaab( rising of the sun ) aur guroob-e-aftaab( before its setting ) se pehle"
  50,40,Aur raat ke waqt phir uski tasbeeh karo aur sajda reizion se faarig honay ke baad bhi(wake of prostration)
  50,41,"Aur suno, jis din munadi (pukaar) karne wala (har shaks ke)qareeb hi se pukarega"
  50,42,"Jis din sab log aawaza-e-hashar ko theek theek sun rahey honge, woh zameen se murdon ke nikalne ka din hoga"
  50,43,"Hum hi zindagi bakshte hain aur hum hi maut detey hain, aur hamari hi taraf us din sabko palatna hai"
  50,44,Jab zameen phategi log uske andar se nikal kar teiz teiz bhage ja rahe honge. Yeh hashar hamare liye bahut aasaan hai
  50,45,"Aey Nabi, jo baatein yeh log bana rahe hain unhein hum khoob jaante hain, aur tumhara kaam inse jabran (zabardasti) baat manwana nahin hai. Bas tum is Quran ke zariye se har us shaks ko nasihat kardo jo meri tambeeh se darey"
  51,1,Kasam hai un hawaon ki jo gard (dust) udane wali hain
  51,2,Phir pani se ladeh huey badal uthane wali hain
  51,3,Phir subuk raftari (smoothly speed along) ke saath chalne wali hain
  51,4,Phir ek baday kaam (barish) ki taqseem karne wali hain
  51,5,Haqq yeh hai ke jis cheez ka tumhein khauf dilaya ja raha hai woh sacchi hai
  51,6,Aur jazaa-e-aamal (recompense) zaroor pesh aani hai
  51,7,Kasam hai muttafarriq shakalon(numerous forms) waley aasmaan ki
  51,8,(Aakhirat ke barey mein) tumhari baat ek durse se mukhtalif hai
  51,9,Ussey wahi bargashta (deluded/averse) hota hai jo haqq se phira hua hai
  51,10,Maarey gaye qayas-o-gumaan (conjecturers) se hukum lagane wale
  51,11,Jo jihalat(ignorance) mein garq aur gaflat mein madhosh hain
  51,12,Puchte hain aakhir woh roz-e-jaza kab aayega
  51,13,Woh us roz aayega jab yeh log aag par tapaye jayenge
  51,14,"(Insey kaha jayega) ab chakkho maza apne fitne ka, yeh wahi cheez hai jiske liye tum jaldi macha rahey thay"
  51,15,Albatta muttaqi log us roz baaghon(gardens) aur chashmo (fountains) mein hongey
  51,16,Jo kuch unka Rubb unhein dega usey khushi khushi le rahey hongey. Woh us din ke aane se pehle neikukar (doers of good) thay
  51,17,Raaton(nights) ko kam hi sotey(sleep) thay
  51,18,Phir wahi raat ke pichle peharon mein maafi maangte thay
  51,19,Aur unke maalon(wealth) mein haqq tha saahil( maangne waley) aur mehroom(destitute) ke liye
  51,20,Zameen mein bahut si nishaniyan hain yaqeen laney walon ke liye
  51,21,"Aur khud tumhare apne wajood mein hain, kya tumko soojhta nahin"
  51,22,Aasman hi mein hai tumhara rizq bhi aur woh cheez bhi jiska tumse waada kiya ja raha hai
  51,23,"Pas kasam hai aasmaan aur zameen ke maalik ki, yeh baat haqq hai, aisi hi yaqeeni jaise tum bol rahey ho"
  51,24,"Aey Nabi, Ibrahim ke muazzaz mehmano ki hiqayat bhi tumhein pahunchi hai"
  51,25,Jab woh uske haan (yahan) aaye to kaha aapko salaam hai. Usne kaha “ aap logon ko bhi salaam hai kuch na-aashna se log hain”
  51,26,"Phir woh chupke se apne ghar walon ke paas gaya, aur ek mota taaza bachda (calf) laa kar"
  51,27,Mehmanon ke aage pesh kiya. Usne kaha aap hazraat khate nahin
  51,28,"Phir woh apne dil mein unse dara. Unhon ne kaha dariye nahin, aur usey ek zee-ilm ladke ki paidaish ka mushda (good news/basharat) sunaya"
  51,29,"Yeh sunkar uski biwi cheekhti hui aage badhi aur usne apna mooh peeth liya aur kehne lagi, “boodhi baanj”"
  51,30,Unhon ne kaha “yahi kuch farmaya hai tere Rubb ne. Woh hakeem hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai
  51,31,"Ibrahim ne kaha “aey farstaadgaan-e-ilaahi (envoys), kya mohim aapko dar-pesh hai"
  51,32,Unhon ne kaha “hum ek mujrim qaum ki taraf bheje gaye hain
  51,33,Taa-ke uspar paki hui mitti ke patthar (clay-stones) barsa de
  51,34,Jo aapke Rubb ke haan hadd se guzar jane walon ke liye nishan zada hain”
  51,35,Phir humne un sab logon ko nikal liya jo us basti mein momin thay
  51,36,Aur wahan humne ek ghar ke siwa musalmano ka koi ghar na paya
  51,37,Uske baad humne wahan bas ek nishani un logon ke liye chodh di jo dardnaak azaab se darte hon
  51,38,Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Moosa ke qissey mein jab humne usey sareeh sanad (clear authority) ke saath Firoun ke paas bheja
  51,39,To woh apne bal-bootay par akad gaya aur bola yeh jaadugar hai ya majnoon(deewana) hai
  51,40,Aakhir-e-kaar humne usey aur uske lashkaron ko pakda aur sabko samandar mein phenk diya aur woh malamat zadah hokar reh gaya
  51,41,"Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Aad (people of Aad) mein, jabke humne unpar ek aisi hi bay-khair(devastating) hawa bhej di"
  51,42,Ke jis cheez par bhi woh guzar gayi usey boseeda (rotten) karke rakh diya
  51,43,"Aur (tumhare liye nishani hai) Samood mein, jab unse kaha gaya tha ke ek khaas waqt tak mazey karlo"
  51,44,Magar is tambeeh(warning) par bhi unhon ne apne Rubb ke hukum se sartabi (brazenly disobey) ki. Aakhir-e-kar unke dekhte dekhte ek achanak toot padne waley azaab ne unko aa liya
  51,45,Phir na unmein uthne ki sakat thi aur na woh apna bachao kar sakte thay
  51,46,Aur in sabse pehle humne Nooh ki qaum ko halaak kiya kyunke woh fasiq (wicked) log thay
  51,47,Aasman ko humne apne zoar se banaya hai aur hum iski qudrat rakhte hain
  51,48,Zameen ko humne bichaya hai aur hum badey acchey hamwar(Smoothers/ spread) karne waley hain
  51,49,"Aur har cheez ke humne jodey banaye hain, shayad ke tum ussey sabaq lo"
  51,50,"To daudo Allah ki taraf , main tumahre liye us ki taraf se saaf saaf khabardar karne wala hoon"
  51,51,Aur na banao Allah ke saath koi dusra mabood. Main tumahre liye uski taraf se saaf saaf khabardar karne wala hoon
  51,52,"Yunhi hota raha hai, inse pehle ki qaumon ke paas bhi koi Rasool aisa nahin aaya jisey unhon ne yeh na kaha ho ke yeh saahir (sorcerer) hai ya majnoon(deewana)"
  51,53,"Kya in sab ne apas mein ispar koi samjhauta karliya hai? Nahin, balke yeh sab sarkash log hain"
  51,54,"Pas aey Nabi, inse rukh pher lo, tumpar kuch malamat nahin"
  51,55,"Albatta nasihat karte raho, kyunke nasihat imaan laney walon ke liye nafeh(faiyda-mand) hai"
  51,56,Maine Jinn aur Insano ko iske siwa kisi kaam ke liye paida nahin kiya hai ke woh meri bandagi karein
  51,57,Main unsey koi rizq nahin chahta aur na yeh chahta hoon ke woh mujhey khilayein
  51,58,"Allah to khud hi Razzak hai, badi quwwat wala aur zabardast"
  51,59,"Pas jin logon ne zulm kiya hai unke hissey ka bhi waisa hi azaab tayyar hai jaisa inhi jaise logon ko unke hissey ka mil chuka hai, iske liye yeh log jaldi na machayein"
  51,60,Aakhir ko tabahi hai kufr karne walon ke liye us roz jiska inhein khauff dilaya jaa raha hai
  52,1,Kasam hai Tur (Mount) ki
  52,2,Aur ek aisi khuli kitaab ki
  52,3,Jo raqeeq jild(fine parchment) mein likkhi hui hai
  52,4,Aur aabaad (much-frequented) ghar ki
  52,5,Aur unchi chatt (canopy) ki
  52,6,Aur maujzan samandar (swelling sea) ki
  52,7,Ke tere Rubb ka azaab zaroor waqeh honay wala hai
  52,8,Jisey koi dafa karne wala nahin
  52,9,Woh us roz waqeh hoga jab aasmaan buri tarah dagmagayega
  52,10,Aur pahad udey udey phirenge
  52,11,Tabahi hai us roz un jhutlane walon ke liye
  52,12,Jo aaj khel ke taur par apni hujjat baaziyon mein lagey huey hain
  52,13,Jis din unhein dhakke maar maar kar naar-e-jahannum (fire of hell) ki taraf le chala jayega
  52,14,Us waqt unse kaha jayega ke “ yeh wahi aag hai jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay
  52,15,Ab batao yeh jaadu hai ya tumhein soojh nahin raha hai
  52,16,"Jao ab jhulso iske andar, tum khwa sabr karo ya na karo, tumhare liye yaksan hai, tumhein waisa hi badla diya ja raha hai jaise tum amal kar rahey thay"
  52,17,Muttaqi log wahan baagon (gardens) aur niyamaton mein hongey
  52,18,"Lutf le rahe hongey un cheezon se jo unka Rubb unhein dega, aur unka Rubb unhein dozakh ke azaab se bacha lega"
  52,19,(Unse kaha jayega) khao aur peo mazey se apne un aamaal ke siley mein jo tum karte rahey ho
  52,20,Woh aamne saamne bichey huey takhaton(thrones) par takiye(couches) lagaye baithey hongey aur hum khoobsurat aankhon waali hoorein unse biyah (marry) denge
  52,21,Jo log imaan laaye hain aur unki aulad bhi kisi darja-e-imaan mein unke naksh-e-qadam par chali hai unki us aulad ko bhi hun (jannat mein) unke saath mila denge aur unke amaal mein koi ghaata(loss) unko na denge. Har shaks apne kasb ke aevaz rehan hai.( Every person is pledged to what he did)
  52,22,"Hum unko har tarah ke phal (fruits) aur gosht , jis cheez ko bhi unka ji chahega khoob diye chale jayenge"
  52,23,Wahan woh ek dusre se jaam-e-sharaab lapak lapak kar le rahey hongey jis mein na yawa-goyi (ill speech) hogi na bad-kirdari
  52,24,"Aur unki khidmat mein woh ladke daudte (running) phir rahey hongey jo unhi ke liye makhsoos hongey, aisey khoobsurat jaise chupa kar rakkhe huey moti(pearls)"
  52,25,Yeh log apas mein ek dusre se (duniya mein guzre huey) halaat puchenge
  52,26,Yeh kahenge ke hum pehle apne ghar waalon mein darte huey zindagi basar karte thay
  52,27,Aakhir e kaar Allah ne hum par fazl farmaya aur humein jhulsa dene wali hawa ke azaab se bacha liya
  52,28,"Hum pichli zindagi mein usi se duaein maangte thay, woh waqai bada hi Mohsin (beneficent) aur Raheem hai"
  52,29,"Pas aey nabi, tum nasihat kiye jao, apne Rubb ke fazal se na tum kaahin (soothsayer) ho aur na majnoon (madman)"
  52,30,Kya yeh log kehte hain ke yeh shaks shayar hai jiske haqq mein hum gardish-e-ayyam (misfortune) ke intizaar kar rahe hain
  52,31,"Inse kaho, accha intizaar karo, main bhi tumhare saath intizaar karta hoon"
  52,32,Kya inki aqalein(minds) inhein aisi hi baatein karne ke liye kehti hain? Ya dar-haqeeqat yeh inaad (transgression)mein hadd se guzare huey log hain
  52,33,Kya ye kehte hain ke is shaks ne yeh quraan khud ghad (invented/fabricated) liya hai? Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh imaan nahin lana chahte
  52,34,Agar yeh apne is qaul (saying) mein sacche hain to isi shaan ka ek kalaam bana layein
  52,35,Kya yeh kisi khaliq ke bagair khud paida ho gaye hain? Ya yeh khud apne khaliq hain
  52,36,Ya zameen aur aasmaano ko inhon ne paida kiya hai? Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh yaqeen nahin rakhte
  52,37,Kya tere Rubb ke khazane in ke kabze mein hain? Ya un par inhi ka hukum chalta hai
  52,38,Kya inke paas koi seedi(ladder) hai jispar chadh kar yeh ilm-e-baala ki sun-gun letey hain? In mein se jisne sun-gun li ho woh laaye ko khuli daleel
  52,39,Kya Allah ke liye to hain betiyan aur tum logon ke liye hain betay (sons)
  52,40,Kya tum insey koi ajar maangte ho key eh zabardasti padi hui chatti ke bojh taley dabey jatey hain (burdened with a load of debt)
  52,41,Kya inke paas gaib ke haqaiq ka ilm hai ke uski bina par yeh likh rahe hoon
  52,42,Kya yeh koi chaal chalna chahte hain? (agar yeh baat hai) to kufr karne walon par in ki chaal ulti hi padegi
  52,43,Kya Allah ke siwa yeh koi aur maabood rakhte hain? Allah paak hai us shirk se jo yeh log kar rahey hain
  52,44,Yeh log aasmaan ke tukde bhi girte huye dekh lein to kahenge yeh baadal hain jo umdey chale aa rahe hain
  52,45,"Pas aey nabi, inhein inke haal par chodh do yahan tak ke yeh apne us din ko pahunch jayein jismein yeh maar giraye jayenge"
  52,46,Jis din na inki apni koi chaal inke kisi kaam aayegi na koi inki madad ko aayega
  52,47,"Aur us waqt ke aane se pehle bhi zalimon ke liye ek azaab hai, magar in mein se aksar jaante nahin hain"
  52,48,"Aey Nabi , apne Rubb ka faisla aane tak sabr karo. Tum hamari nigaah mein ho. Tum jab utho to apne Rubb ki hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo"
  52,49,Raat ko bhi uski tasbeeh kiya karo aur sitare jab palat-te hain us waqt bhi
  53,1,Kasam hai taare ki jabke woh guroob hua
  53,2,Tumhara rafeeq(companion) na bhatka hai na behka(deluded) hai
  53,3,Woh apni khwaish-e-nafs se nahin bolta
  53,4,Yeh to ek wahee (Inspiration /revelation) hai jo uspar nazil ki jati hai
  53,5,Usey zabardast quwwat waley ne taleem di hai
  53,6,Jo bada sahib-e-hikmat hai
  53,7,Woh saamne aa khada hua jabke woh balaii ufuq par tha(highest part of the horizon)
  53,8,Phir kareeb aaya aur upar muallak ho gaya.(approached and descended)
  53,9,Yahan tak ke do kamano (bow lengths) ke barabar ya issey kuch kam faasla reh gaya
  53,10,Tab usne Allah ke banday ko wahee (revelation) pahunchayi jo wahee (revelation) bhi usey pahunchani thi
  53,11,"Nazar ne jo kuch dekha, dil ne usmein jhoot na milaya"
  53,12,Ab kya tum us cheez par ussey jhagadte ho jisey woh aankhon se dekhta hai
  53,13,Aur ek martaba phir usney
  53,14,Sidratul muntaha ke paas usko (Angel Gibriel) dekha
  53,15,Jahan paas hi jannat-ul-maawa hai
  53,16,Us waqt sidrah par chaa raha tha jo kuch ke chaa raha tha
  53,17,Nigaah na chundhyayi (waver / swerve) na hadd se mutajawiz (transgress) hui
  53,18,Aur usney apne Rubb ki badi badi nishaniyan dekhi
  53,19,"Ab zara batao , tumne kabhi is Laat aur is Uzza (names of pagan idols)"
  53,20,Aur tisri (third) ek aur devi Manaat ki haqeeqat par kuch gaur bhi kiya
  53,21,Kya betay (sons) tumhare liye hain aur betiyan (daughters) khuda ke liye
  53,22,Yeh to badi dhandhli (unjust/unfair) ki taqseem hui
  53,23,"Darasal yeh kuch nahin hain magar bas chandh naam jo tumne aur tumhare baap dada ne rakh liye hain. Allah ne inke liye koi sanad nazil nahin ki. Haqeeat yeh hai ke log mehez weham-o-gumaan ki pairvi kar rahey hain aur khwahishaat-e-nafs ke mureed bane huey hain, halanke unke Rubb ki taraf se unke paas hidayat aa chuki hai"
  53,24,Kya insaan jo kuch chaahe uske liye wahi haqq hai
  53,25,Duniya aur aakhirat ka maalik to Allah hi hai
  53,26,"Aasmano mein kitne hi farishte maujood hain, un ki shafaat (intercession) kuch bhi kaam nahin aa sakti jab tak ke Allah kisi aisey shaks ke haqq mein uski ijazat na dey jiske liye woh koi arzdaasht (plea) sunna chahe aur usko pasand karey"
  53,27,Magar jo log aakhirat ko nahin maante woh farishton ko deviyon (godess) ke naamo se mausoom karte hain
  53,28,"Halaanke is maamle ka koi ilm (knowledge) unhein haasil nahin hai. Woh mehez gumaan ki pairvi kar rahey hain, aur gumaan haqq ki jagah kuch bhi kaam nahin de sakta"
  53,29,"Pas aey Nabi, jo shaks hamarey zikr se mooh pherta hai, aur duniya ki zindagi ke siwa jise kuch matloob nahin hai, usey uske haal par chodh do"
  53,30,"In logon ka mablag-e-ilm (utmost of their knowledge) bas yahi kuch hai, yeh baat tera Rubb hi zyada jaanta hai ke uske raaste se kaun bhatak gaya hai aur kaun seedhe raaste par hai"
  53,31,Aur zameen aur aasmaano ki har cheez ka maalik Allah hi hai. Taa-ke Allah burayi karne waalon ko unke amal ka badla de aur un logon ko acchi jaza se nawaze jinhon ne neik rawayya ikhtiyar kiya hai
  53,32,"Jo badey badey gunahon aur khule khule qabeeh afaal (shameful deeds) se parheiz karte hain, illa yeh ke kuch kasoor unse sarzad ho jaye. Bila shubhah tere Rubb ka daaman-e-magfirat bahut waseeh hai. Woh tumhein us waqt se khoob jaanta hai jab usne zameen se tumhein paida kiya, aur jab tum apni maaon (mothers) ke paiton (wombs) mein abhi janin (fetuses) hi thay. Pas apne nafs ki paaki ke daawe na karo. Wahi behtar jaanta hai ke waqai muttaqi kaun hai"
  53,33,"Phir aey Nabi, tumne us shaks ko bhi dekha jo raah-e-khuda se phir gaya"
  53,34,Aur thoda sa de kar ruk gaya
  53,35,Kya uske paas gaib ka ilm hai ke woh haqeeqat ko dekh raha hai
  53,36,Kya usey un baaton ki koi khabar nahin pahunchi jo moosa ke sahifon
  53,37,Aur us Ibrahim ke sahifon mein bayan hui hai jisne wafa ka haqq ada kar diya
  53,38,Yeh ke koi bojh uthane wala dusre ka bojh nahin uthayega
  53,39,Aur yeh ke Insaan ke liye kuch nahin hai magar woh jiski usne saii(koshish /Strive) ki hai
  53,40,Aur yeh ke uski saii (koshih/strive/effort) anqareeb dekhi jayegi
  53,41,Aur uski puri jaza use di jayegi
  53,42,Aur yeh ke aakhir-e-kaar pahunchna tere Rubb hi ke paas hai
  53,43,Aur yeh ke usi ne hasaya aur usi ne rulaya
  53,44,Aur yeh ke usi ne maut di aur usi ne zindagi bakshi
  53,45,Aur yeh ke usi ne narr (male) aur maada (female) ka joda paida kiya
  53,46,Ek boond (sperm-drop) se jab woh tapkayi jati hai
  53,47,Aur yeh ke dusri zindagi bakshna bhi usi ke zimme hai
  53,48,Aur yeh ke usi ne gani (enriches) kiya aur jaidad bakshi
  53,49,Aur yeh ke wahi sheraa (Sirius / mighty star) ka Rubb hai
  53,50,Aur yeh ke usi ne Aad-e-oola (people of Aad) ko halaak kiya
  53,51,Aur samood ko aisa mitaya ke unmein se kisi ko baaki na choda
  53,52,Aur unse pehle qaum-e-Nooh ko tabaah kiya kyunke woh thay hi sakht zaalim-o-sarkash log
  53,53,Aur aundhi girne wali bastiyon ko utha phenka. (Qaum-e-Lut)
  53,54,Phir chaa diya unpar woh kuch jo (tum jaante hi ho ke) kya chaa diya
  53,55,"Pas aey mukhatib, apne Rubb ki kin kin niyamaton mein tu shakk karega"
  53,56,Yeh ek tambeeh (warning) hai pehle aaye huye tambihaat(warnings) mein se
  53,57,Aane wali ghadi qareeb aa lagi hai
  53,58,Allah ke siwa koi usko hatane wala nahin
  53,59,Ab kya yahi woh baatein hain jinpar tum izhaar- e-taajub karte ho
  53,60,Hanste(laugh) ho aur rotey (weep) nahin ho
  53,61,Aur gaa (singing) bajaa kar inhein taalte ho
  53,62,Jhuk jao Allah ke aagey aur bandagi baja laaoo (ayat-e-sajda)
  54,1,Qayamat ki ghadi kareeb aa gayi aur chaand phatt (split) gaya
  54,2,Magar in logon ka haal yeh hai ke khwa koi nishani dekh lein mooh moadh jaatey hain aur kehte hain yeh to chalta hua jaadu hai
  54,3,Inhon ne (isko bhi) jhutla diya aur apni khwahishat-e-nafs hi ki pairwi ki.Har maamlay ko Aakhir-e-kaar ek anjaam par pahunch kar rehna hai
  54,4,In logon ke saamne (pichle qaumon ke) woh halaat aa chuke hain jinmein sarkashi se baaz rakhne ke liye kafi samaan-e-ibrat hai
  54,5,Aur aisi hikmat jo nasihat ke maqsad ko ba-darja-e-atam (consummate wisdom) pura karti hain magar tambihat(warnings) in par kaargar nahin hoti
  54,6,"Pas aey Nabi, insey rukh pher lo. Jis roz pukarne wala ek sakht nagawaar cheez ki taraf pukarega"
  54,7,Log sehmi hui (down-cast) nigaahon ke saath apni qabraon se is tarah niklenge goya woh bikhri huyi tiddiyan (locusts) hain
  54,8,Pukarne wale ki taraf daudey jaa rahey hongey Aur wahi munkireen (jo duniya mein iska inkar karte thay)us waqt kahenge ke yeh din to bada kathin hai
  54,9,"Insey pehle Nooh ki qaum jhutla chuki hai. Unhon ne hamare bandey ko jhoota karar diya aur kaha ke yeh deewana hai, aur woh buri tarah jhidka (rebuffed) gaya"
  54,10,"Aakhir-e-kaar usne apne Rubb ko pukara ke “main magloob ho chuka , ab tu inse inteqam le”"
  54,11,Tab humne mausla-dhaar baarish se aasmaan ke darwaze khol diye aur zameen ko phaad kar chasmon mein tabdeel kar diya
  54,12,Aur yeh saara paani us kaam ko pura karne ke liye mil gaya jo mukaddar ho chuka tha
  54,13,Aur Nooh ko humne ek takhaton(planks) aur keelon (nails) wali par sawar kar diya
  54,14,Jo hamari nigrani mein chal rahi thi .yeh tha badla us shaks ki khatir jiski na-qadri ki gayi thi
  54,15,"Us kashti ko humne ek nishani bana kar chodh diya, phir koi hai nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,16,"Dekhlo, kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)"
  54,17,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,18,"Aad ne jhutlaya, to dekhlo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)"
  54,19,Humne ek paiham nahusat (unremitting misfortune) ke din sakht toofani hawa unpar bhej di jo logon ko utha utha kar is tarah phenk rahi thi
  54,20,Jaise woh jadd (roots) se ukhade huey khajoor ke taney (trunks) hon
  54,21,Pas dekhlo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambihaat (warnings)
  54,22,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, phir kya hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,23,Samood ne tambihaat ko jhutlaya
  54,24,Aur kehne lagey “Ek akela aadmi jo hum hi mein se hai kya ab hum uske peechey chalein? Iska ittibaah hum qabool karlein to iske maani yeh hongey ke hum behak gaye hain aur hamari aqal maari gayi hai
  54,25,"Kya hamare darmiyan bas yahi ek shaks tha jispar khuda ka zikr nazil kiya gaya? nahin, balke yeh parle darje ka jhoota aur bar-khud galat (insolent liar)hai”"
  54,26,(Humne apne paigambar se kaha) “ Kal hi inhein maaloom hua jata hai ke kaun parle darje ka jhoota aur bar khud galat hai
  54,27,"Hum ountni (she-camel) ko inke liye fitna bana kar bhej rahe hain, ab zara sabr ke saath dekh ke inka kya anjaam hota hai"
  54,28,Inko jata de ke paani inke aur ountni(she-camel) ke darmiyaan takseem hoga aur har ek apni baari ke din paani par aayega”
  54,29,Aakhir-e-kaar un logon ne apne aadmi ko pukara aur usne is kaam ka beda uthaya aur ountni (she-camel) ko maar dala
  54,30,Phir dekh lo ke kaisa tha mera azaab aur kaisi thi meri tambeehat (warnings)
  54,31,"Humne unpar bas ek hi dhamaka chodha aur woh baade wale ki rondhi hui baad ke taraah bhus ho kar reh gaya. (Lo! We sent upon them one Shout, and they became as the dry twigs (rejected by) the builder of a cattle-fold"
  54,32,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, ab hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,33,Lut ki qaum ne tambihat ko jhutlaya
  54,34,Aur humne pattharao karne wali hawa is par bhej di. Sirf Lut ke ghar wale ussey mehfooz rahe
  54,35,Unko humne apne fazl se raat ke pichle pehar bacha kar nikal diya. Yeh jaza dete hai hum har us shaks ko jo shukar guzar hota hai
  54,36,Lut ne apni qaum ke logon ko hamari pakad se khabardaar kiya magar woh saari tambihat ko mashkuk (doubtful) samajh kar baaton mein udate rahey
  54,37,"Phir unhon ne usey apne mehmano ki hifazat se baaz rakhne ki koshish ki. Aakhir-e-kaar humne unki aankhein moond-di (blinded), ke chakkho ab mera azaab aur meri tambihaat ka maza"
  54,38,Subah sawerey hi ek atal azaab ne unko aa liya
  54,39,Chakkho mazaa ab mere azaab ka aur meri tambihaat ka
  54,40,"Humne is Quran ko nasihat ke liye aasaan zariya bana diya hai, pas hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala"
  54,41,Aur aal-e-Firoun ke paas bhi tambihaat aayi thi
  54,42,Magar unhon ne hamari saari nishaniyon ko jhutla diya. Aakhir ko humne unhein pakda jis taraah koi zabardast qudrat wala pakadta hai
  54,43,Kya tumhare kuffar kuch un logon se behtar hain? Ya aasmani kitaabon mein tumhare liye koi maafi likhi hui hai
  54,44,"Ya in logon ka kehna yeh hai ke hum ek mazboot jattha (jamaat) hain, apna bachao kar lengey"
  54,45,Ankareeb yeh jattha(jamaat) shikhast kha jayega aur yeh sab peeth pheir kar bhaagte nazar aayenge
  54,46,Balke insey nimatne ke liye asal waade ka waqt to qayamat hai aur woh badi aafat aur zyaada talkh-saa-at (badi sakht aur kadwi cheez) hai
  54,47,Yeh mujrim log dar haqeeqat galat fehmi mein mubtala hain aur inki aqal maari gayi hai
  54,48,Jis roz yeh mooh ke bal aag mein ghaseetey jayenge us roz insey kaha jayega ke ab chakkho jahannum ki lapat ka maza
  54,49,Humne har cheez ek taqdeer ke saath paida ki hai
  54,50,Aur hamara hukum bas ek hi hukum hota hai aur palak jhapakate (twinkling of an eye) woh amal mein aa jata hai
  54,51,Tum jaisey bahut-soon ko hum halak kar chuke hain. Phir hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala
  54,52,Jo kuch inhon ne kiya hai woh sab daftaron (office) mein darj hai
  54,53,Aur har choti badi baat likhi hui maujood hai
  54,54,Nafarmani se parhez karne waley yaqeenan baaghon aur neharon mein hongey
  54,55,"Sacchi izzat ki jagah, badey zeeh-iqtedar baadshah ke kareeb"
  55,1,Rahman ne
  55,2,Is Quran ki taleem di hai
  55,3,Usi ne Insan ko paida kiya
  55,4,Aur usey bolna sikhaya
  55,5,Suraj aur chand ek hisaab ke paband hain
  55,6,Aur taarey aur darakht sab sajda-reiz hain
  55,7,Aasman ko usne buland kiya aur mizan qayam kardi
  55,8,Iska taqaza yeh hai ke tum mizaan mein khalal na daalo
  55,9,Insaaf ke saath theek theek tolo (weigh) aur tarazu mein dandi (skimp ) na maaro
  55,10,Zameen ko usne sab makhlooqat (creatures) ke liye banaya
  55,11,"Usmein har tarah ke ba-kasrat laziz phal hain,khajoor ke darakht hain jinke phal ghilafon (sheaths) mein liptey huey hain"
  55,12,Tarah tarah ke galley(corn) hain jinmein bhusa bhi hota hai aur dana (grain) bhi
  55,13,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ki kin kin niyamaton ko jhutlaogey"
  55,14,"Insan ko usne thikri (potter) jaise sukhey sadey (rotten) huey gaarey se banaya (clay like [that of] pottery"
  55,15,Aur Jinn ko aag ki lapat se paida kiya
  55,16,"Pas aey Jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ke kin kin ajaib-e-qudrat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,17,"Dono mashriq aur dono magrib, Sab ka maalik-o-parwardigar wahi hai"
  55,18,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins, tum apne Rubb ke kin kin qudraton ko jhutlaogey"
  55,19,Do samandaron (seas) ko usne chodh diya ke baham mil jayein
  55,20,Phir bhi unke darmiyan ek purdah hayal(barrier) hai jissey woh tajawuz (transgress) nahin karte
  55,21,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), Tum apne Rubb ki qudrat ke kin kin karishmo ko jhutlaogey"
  55,22,In samandaron se Moti aur mongay (coral) nikalte hain
  55,23,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ki qudrat ke kin kin kamalaat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,24,Aur yeh jahaaz (ships) usi ke hain jo samandar mein pahadon (mountains) ki tarah unchey uthey huey hain
  55,25,"Pas aye jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rub ke kin kin ehsanaat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,26,Har cheez jo is zameen par hai fanaa (perish) ho janey wali hai
  55,27,Aur sirf tere Rubb ki jalil-o-kareem zaat hi baaki rehne wali hai
  55,28,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ke qudraton ke kin kin kamalaat ko jhutlaogey"
  55,29,"Zameen aur Aasmano mein jo bhi hai sab apni haajatein (needs) usi se maang rahey hain, har aan woh nayi shaan mein hai"
  55,30,"Pas aey jinn-o-Ins (insan), tum apne Rubb ki kin kin siffat-e-hameeda ko jhutlaogey"
  55,31,"Aey zameen ke bojho(loads), ankareeb hum tumse baaz purs (questioning) karne ke liye faarig huey jatey hain"
  55,32,(phir dekh lenge ke) tum apne Rubb ke kin kin ehsanaat ko jhutlate ho
  55,33,"Aey giroh-e-jinn-o-Ins(insan) , gar tum zameen aur aasmano ki sarhadon se nikal kar bhaag sakte ho to bhaag dekho , nahin bhaag sakte iske liye bada zoar chahiye"
  55,34,Apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,35,(Bhaagne ki koshish karogey to ) Tumpar aag ka shola aur dhoowan (smoke) chodh diya jayega jiska tum muqabla na kar sakogey
  55,36,"Pas aey Jinn-o-Ins (insan),tum apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ka inkar karogey"
  55,37,Phir (kya banegi us waqt) jab aasman phatega (split) aur laal chamdey (skin) ki tarah surkh (red) ho jayega
  55,38,Aey Jinn-o-Ins (insan) (us waqt) tum apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ko jhutlaogey
  55,39,Us roz kisi Insan aur kisi Jinn se uska gunaah puchne ke zaroorat na hogi
  55,40,Phir (dekh liya jayega ke) tum dono giroh apne Rubb ke kin kin ehsanaat ka inkar karte ho
  55,41,Mujrim wahan apne chehron se pehchan liye jayenge aur unhein peshani ke baal aur paaon pakad pakad kar ghasita jayega
  55,42,Us waqt tum apne Rub ki kin kin qudraton ko jhutlaogey
  55,43,(Us waqt kaha jayega) yeh wahi jahannum hai jisko mujrimeen jhoot karar diya karte thay
  55,44,Usi jahannum aur khaulte (boiling) paani ke darmiyan woh gardish karte rahenge
  55,45,Phir apne Rubb ki kin kin qudraton ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,46,"Aur har us shaks ke liye jo apne Rubb ke huzoor pesh hone ka khauf(darr) rakhta ho, do baagh (gardens) hain"
  55,47,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,48,Hari bhari daaliyon se bharpur
  55,49,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,50,Dono baaghon(gardens) mein do chashmey (springs) rawan
  55,51,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,52,Dono baaghon(gardens) mein har phal ki do qismein
  55,53,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,54,"Jannati log aisey farshon par takiye laga ke baithenge jinke astar dabiz resham ( silk brocade) ke hongey, Aur baagon ki daliyan phalon se jhuki padh rahi hongi"
  55,55,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,56,In niyamaton ke darmiyan sharmili nigahon waliyan hongi jinhein in jannatiyon se pehle kisi insaan ya Jinn ne chuwa na hoga
  55,57,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,58,Aisi khoobsurat jaisey hirey(diamonds) aur Moti
  55,59,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,60,Neki ka badla neki ke siwa aur kya ho sakta hai
  55,61,"Phir aey Jinn-o-Ins (Insan),apne Rubb ke kin kin awsaaf-e-hameeda ka tum inkar karogey"
  55,62,Aur un do baaghon ke alawa do baagh aur hongey
  55,63,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,64,Ghaney sar-sabz o shadaab baagh
  55,65,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,66,Dono baaghon mein do chashmey (springs) fawwaron ki tarah ubaltey (gushing) huey
  55,67,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,68,Un mein ba-kasrat phal aur khajurein aur anaar (pomegranates)
  55,69,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,70,In niyamaton ke darmiyan khoob seerat aur khoobsurat biwiyan
  55,71,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,72,Kheymo (tents) mein theharayi hui hoorein (maidens)
  55,73,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,74,In jannatiyon se pehle kabhi kisi Insaan ya jinn ne unko na chuwa (touch) hoga
  55,75,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,76,Woh jannati sabz-qaleeno (green cushions) aur nafees o nadir farshon (beautiful carpets) par takiye laga ke baithenge
  55,77,Apne Rubb ke kin kin inaamaat ko tum jhutlaogey
  55,78,Badi barkat wala hai tere Rubb-e-Jaleel-o-Kareem (Majesty and Glory) ka naam
  56,1,Jab woh honay wala waqia pesh aa jayega
  56,2,To koi uske waquh(occurrence) ko jhutlane wala na hoga
  56,3,Woh tah-o-bala (pasth aur buland) kardene wali aafat hogi
  56,4,Zameen us waqt ek baar hi hila daali jayegi
  56,5,Aur pahad is tarah reza reza kardiye jayenge
  56,6,Ke paraganda (scattered) gubar (dust) ban kar reh jayenge
  56,7,Tum log us waqt teen girohon (jamaat) mein taqseem ho jaogey
  56,8,"Dayein bazu waley, so dayein bazu walon (ke khush-naseebi ) ka kya kehna"
  56,9,"Aur bayein bazu waley, to bayein bazu walon (ki badnasibi ka) kya thikana"
  56,10,Aur aagey waley to phir aagey waley hi hain
  56,11,Wahi to muqarrab (nearest to Allah) log hain
  56,12,Niyamat bhari jannaton mein rahengey
  56,13,Aglon mein se bahut hongey
  56,14,Aur pichlon mein se kam
  56,15,Murassasa takhaton par (On thrones decorated)
  56,16,Takiye lagaye aamne saamne baithengey
  56,17,Unki majlison mein abadi ladke sharab-e-chashma-e jaari se
  56,18,Labrez pyale aur kantar (jugs) aur saagar liye daudte phirte hongey
  56,19,Jisey pee kar na unka sar chakrayega na unki aqal mein fatur (drunkenness) aayega
  56,20,Aur woh unke saamne tarah tarah ke lazeez phal (fruits) pesh karengey jisey chahe chun le
  56,21,Aur parindon ke gosht pesh karenge ke jis parinde ka chahein istimal karein
  56,22,Aur unke liye khubsurat aankhon wali hoorein hongi
  56,23,Aisi haseen jaise chupa kar rakkhey huey moti
  56,24,Yeh sab kuch un aamal ki jaza ke taur par unhein milega jo woh duniya mein karte rahe thay
  56,25,Wahan woh koi behuda kalaam ya gunah ki baat na sunengey
  56,26,Jo baat bhi hogi theek theek hogi
  56,27,"Aur daayein bazu waley, daayein bazu walon ki khush nasibi ka kya kehna"
  56,28,Woh be-khaar (thornless) beriyon(lote trees)
  56,29,Aur teh bar teh chadey huey kelon (bananas)
  56,30,Aur door tak phayli hui chaaon (shadow)
  56,31,Aur har dum rawan (gushing) paani
  56,32,Aur kabhi khatam na honay waley
  56,33,Aur bay rok-tok milne waley ba-kasrat phalon (fruits)
  56,34,Aur unchi nishist gaahon (exalted thrones) mein hongay
  56,35,Unki biwiyon ko hum khaas taur par naye sirey se paida karengey
  56,36,Aur unhein bakira (virgins) bana dengey
  56,37,Apne shoharon ki aashik aur umar mein humsin (equal age)
  56,38,Yeh kuch daayein bazu walon ke liye hai
  56,39,Woh aglon mein se bahut hongey
  56,40,Aur pichlon mein se bhi bahut
  56,41,"Aur baayein (left) bazu wale, bayein bazu walon ki badnasibi ka kya puchna"
  56,42,Woh luu ki lapat (midst of scorching wind) aur khaulte (boiling) huey paani
  56,43,Aur kaalay dhuwon (smoke) ke saaye mein hongey
  56,44,Jo na thanda hoga na aaram de
  56,45,Yeh woh log hongey jo is anjaam ko pahunchne se pehle khush haal thay
  56,46,Aur gunaah-e-azeem par israr karte thay
  56,47,Kehte thay “kya jab hum mar kar khaak ho jayengey aur haddiyon ka panjar reh jayengey to phir utha khadey kiye jayenge
  56,48,Aur kya hamare woh baap dada bhi uthaye jayengey jo pehle guzar chuke hain?”
  56,49,"Aye Nabi in logon se kaho, yaqeenan agle aur pichle sab"
  56,50,Ek din zaroor jama kiye janey wale hain jiska waqt muqarrar kiya ja chuka hai
  56,51,Phir aey gumrahon aur jhutlane walon
  56,52,Tum shajar-e-zaqqum ki giza khane waley ho
  56,53,Usi se tum pait bharogey
  56,54,Aur upar se khaulta (boiling) hua paani
  56,55,Toans (thirst) lagey huey ount (camel) ki tarah piogey
  56,56,Yahi baayein walon ki ziyafat ka saamaan roz-e-jaza mein
  56,57,Humne tumhein paida kiya hai phir kyun tasdeek (confirm) nahin karte
  56,58,"Kabhi tumne gaur kiya, yeh nutfa (sperm) jo tum daltey ho"
  56,59,Usse baccha tum banate ho ya uske banane wale hum hain
  56,60,"Humne tumharey darmiyan maut ko takseem kiya hai, aur hum issey aajiz nahin hai"
  56,61,Ke tumhari shaklein badal dein aur kisi aisi shakal mein tumhein paida kardein jisko tum nahin jante
  56,62,"Apni pehli paidaish ko to tum jante ho, phir kyun sabaq nahin letay"
  56,63,"Kabhi tumne socha, yeh beej (seed) jo tum botey ho"
  56,64,Insey khetiyan tum ugatey ho ya unke ugane waley hum hain
  56,65,Hum chahein to un khetoun ko bhus (rubble) bana kar rakh dein aur tum tarah tarah ki baatein banate reh jao
  56,66,Ke hum par to ulti chatti pad gayi (Lo! we are laden with debt)
  56,67,Balke humarey to naseeb hi phootey huey hain
  56,68,"Kabhi tumne aankhein khol kar dekha, yeh paani jo tum peetey ho"
  56,69,Isey tumne baadal se barsaya hai ya iske barsane wale hum hain
  56,70,"Hum chahein to isey sakht khari(bitter) bana kar rakh dein, phir kyun tum shukar guzar nahin hotey"
  56,71,"Kabhi tumne khayal kiya, yeh aag jo tum sulgate ho"
  56,72,Iska darakht tum ne paida kiya hai ya iske paida karne wale hum hain
  56,73,Humne usko yaad-dihani(reminder) ka zariya aur haajat-mandon (needy) ke liye saaman-e-zeist (provision) banaya hai
  56,74,"Pas aey Nabi, apne Rubb-e-azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
  56,75,"Pas nahin main kasam khata hoon taaron ke mawake (setting or the mansions, etc.) ki"
  56,76,Agar tum samjho to yeh bahut badi qasam hai
  56,77,Ke yeh ek buland paya Quran hai
  56,78,Ek mehfooz kitaab mein sabt (inscribed)
  56,79,Jisey mutahreen (pure) ke siwa koi choo nahin sakta
  56,80,Yeh Rubb-ul- Aalameen ka nazil karda hai
  56,81,Phir kya is kalam ke saath tum be-atnayi (indifferent) barat-te ho
  56,82,Aur is niyamat mein apna hissa tumne yeh rakkha hai ke isey jhutlate ho
  56,83,To jab marne wale ki jaan halaq tak pahunch chuki hoti hai
  56,84,Aur tum aankhon se dekh rahe hotey ho ke woh marr raha hai
  56,85,Us waqt tumhare ba-nisbat hum uske zyada kareeb hotey hain magar tumko nazar nahin aatey
  56,86,Ab agar tum kisi ke mahkoom(anyones authority) nahin ho aur apne is khayal mein sacchey ho
  56,87,Us waqt uski nikalti hui jaan ko wapas kyun nahin ley aatey
  56,88,Phir woh marne wala agar muqarrabin (near to Allah) mein se hon
  56,89,To uske liye rahat aur umda rizq aur niyamat bhari jannat hai
  56,90,Aur agar woh ashaab-e-yameen mei se ho
  56,91,"To uska istaqbal (welcome) yun hota hai ke salaam hai tujhey, tu ashab-ul-yameen (People on the Right) mein se hai"
  56,92,Aur agar woh jhutlane waley gumraah logon mein se ho
  56,93,To uski tawazu ke liye khaulta (boiling) pani hai
  56,94,Aur jahannum mein jhonka jaana
  56,95,Yeh sab kuch qataii haqq hai
  56,96,Pas aey Nabi apne Rubb-e-Azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo
  57,1,"Allah ki tasbeeh ki hai har us cheez ne jo zameen aur aasmano mein hai, Aur wahi zabardast daana (wise) hai"
  57,2,"Zameen aur aasmano ki sultanat ka maalik wahi hai, zindagi bakshta hai aur maut deta hai, aur har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  57,3,"Wahi awwal bhi hai aur aakhir bhi, aur zaahir bhi hai aur makhfi(hiddin) bhi , aur woh har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
  57,4,"Wahi hai jisne aasmano aur zameen ko chey (six) dino mein paida kiya aur phir arsh par jalwa farma hua. Uske ilm mein hai jo kuch zameen mein jata hai aur jo kuch ussey nikalta hai, aur jo kuch aasman se utarta hai aur jo kuch usmein chadhta hai. Woh tumhare saath hai jahan bhi tum ho. Jo kaam bhi karte ho usey woh dekh raha hai"
  57,5,Wahi zameen aur aasmano ki baadshahi ka maalik hai aur tamaam maamlaat faisley ke liye usi ki taraf ruju kiye jatey hain
  57,6,"Wahi raat ko din mein aur din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai, aur dilon ke chupey huye raaz tak janta hai"
  57,7,Iman lao Allah aur uske Rasool par aur kharch karo un cheezon mein se jinpar usney tumko khalifa banaya hai. Jo log tum mein se iman layenge aur maal kharch karenge unke liye bada ajr hai
  57,8,"Tumhein kya ho gaya hai ke tum Allah par iman nahin latey halanke Rasool tumhein apne Rubb par iman laney ki dawat de raha hai, aur woh tumse ahad (covenant) le chuka hai, agar tum waqayi maanne waley ho"
  57,9,Woh Allah hi to hai jo apne banday par saaf saaf aayatein nazil kar raha hai taa-ke tumhein tareekhiyon (darkness) se nikal kar roshni mein le aaye. Aur haqeeat yeh hai ke Allah tumpar nihayat shafeeq aur meharbaan hai
  57,10,Aakhir kya wajah hai ke tum Allah ki raah mein kharch nahin karte halanke zameen aur aasmano ki miraas (inheritance) Allah hi ke liye hai. Tum mein se jo log fatah ke baad kharch aur jihad karenge woh kabhi un logon ke barabar nahin ho sakte jinhon ne fatah se pehle kharch aur jihad kiya hai.Unka darja baad mein kharch aur jihad karne walon se badh-kar hai hai agarche Allah ne dono hi se acchey waade famaye hain. Jo kuch tum karte ho Allah ussey ba-khabar hai
  57,11,Kaun hai jo Allah ko qarz dey? Accha qarz taa-ke Allah usey kai gunaa bada kar wapas dey. Aur uske liye behtareen ajar hai
  57,12,"Us din jabke tum momin mardon aur auraton ko dekhoge ke unka noor unke aagey aagey aur unke dayein jaanib daud raha hoga (unse kaha jayega ke) aaj basharat (khushkhabri) hai. Tumhare liye jannatein hongi jinke nichey nehrein beh rahi hongi, jin mein woh hamesha rahenge. Yahi hai badi kamiyabi"
  57,13,"Us roz munafik mardon aur auraton ka haal yeh hoga ke woh momino se kahenge zara hamari taraf dekho taa-ke hum tumhare noor se kuch fayda uthayein. Magar unse kaha jayega pichey hatt jao, Apna noor kahin aur talash karo. Phir unke darmiyan ek deewar hayal kardi jayegi jismein ek darwaza hoga us darwaze ke andar rehmat hogi aur bahar azaab"
  57,14,"Woh momino se pukar pukar kar kahenge kya hum tumhare saath na thay? Momin jawab dengey haan, magar tumne apne aap ko khud fitne mein dala, mauqa parasti ki, shakk mein padey rahey, aur jhooti tawakkuat (expectations) tumhein fareb deti rahi Yahan tak ke Allah ka faisla aa gaya. Aur aakhri waqt tak woh bada dhoke baaz tumhein Allah ke maamle mein dhoka deta raha"
  57,15,Lihaza aaj na tumse koi fidiya kabool kiya jayega aur na un logon se jinhon ne khula khula kufr kiya tha. Tumhara thikana jahannum hai. Wahi tumhari khabar-giri karne wali hai aur yeh badtareen anjaam hai
  57,16,"Kya iman laney walon ke liye abhi woh waqt nahin aaya ke unke dil Allah ke zikr se pighlein aur uske nazil karda haqq ke aagey jhukein aur woh un logon ki tarah na ho jayein jinhein pehle kitaab di gayi thi, phir ek lambi muddat unpar guzar gayi to unke dil sakht ho gaye aur aaj unmein se aksar fasiq banay huey hain"
  57,17,"Khoob jaan lo ke Allah zameen ko uski maut ke baad zindagi bakshta hai, humne nishaniyan tumko saaf saaf dikha di hai, shayad ke tum aqal se kaam lo"
  57,18,"Mardon aur auraton mein se jo log sadaqaat (charity) dene waley hain aur jinhon ne Allah ko karz-e-hasan diya hai, unko yakeenan kayi gunaa bada kar diya jayega aur unke liye behtareen ajar hai"
  57,19,Aur jo log Allah aur uske Rasoolon par iman laye hain wahi apne Rubb ke nazdeek siddiq aur shaheed hain. Unke liye unka ajar aur unka noor hai. Aur jin logon ne kufr kiya hai aur hamari aayat ko jhutlaya hai woh dozakhi hai
  57,20,Khoob jaan lo ke yeh duniya ki zindagi iske siwa kuch nahin ke ek khel aur dil-lagi aur zaahiri tip top aur tumhara aapas mein ek dusre par fakr jatana aur maal-o-aulad mein ek dusre se badh janey ki koshish karna hai.Iski misal aisi hai jaise ek baarish ho gayi to usse paida honay wali nabataat(vegetation) ko dekh kar kaasht-kaar (kisan) khush ho gaye. Phir wahi kheti pak jati hai aur tum dekhte ho ke woh zard (yellow) ho gayi phir woh bhus (chura chura /crumble) bankar reh jati hai. Iske baraks aakhirat woh jagah hai jahan sakht azaab hai aur Allah ki magfirat aur uski khushnudi hai. Dunkya ki zindagi ek dhoke ke tatti (means of deception) ke siwa kuch nahin
  57,21,"Daudo (race) aur ek dusrey se aage badhne ki koshish karo apne Rubb ki magfirat aur uski jannat ki taraf jiski wussat (width) aasman-o-zameen jaisi hai. Jo muhayya ki gayi hai un logon ke liye jo Allah aur uske Rasoolon par iman laye hon. Yeh Allah ka fazl hai, jisey chahta hai ata farmata hai, aur Allah badey fazl wala hai"
  57,22,Koi museebat aisi nahin hai jo zameen mein ya tumhare apne nafs par nazil hoti ho aur humne usko paida karne se pehle ek kitaab mein likh na rakkha ho. Aisa karna Allah ke liye bahut aasaan kaam hai
  57,23,(Yeh sab kuch isliye hai) taa-ke jo kuch bhi nuksaan tumhein ho us par tum dil-shikasta (grieve) na hon aur jo kuch Allah tumhein ata farmaye uspar phool na jao. Allah aisey logon ko pasand nahin karta jo apne aap ko badi cheez samajhte hain aur fakr jatate hain
  57,24,Jo khud bukhl (niggard/kanjusi) karte hain aur dusron ko bukhl par uksate hain. Ab agar koi ru-gardani (mooh pherna) karta hai to Allah be-niyaz aur satoda siffat (immensely praiseworthy) hai
  57,25,"Humne apne Rasoolon ko saaf saaf nishaniyon aur hidayaat ke saath bheja, aur unke saath kitaab aur mizaan (balance) nazil ki taakay log insaf par qayam hon. Aur loha (Iron) utara jis mein bada zoar hai aur logon ke liye munafa hai. Yeh isliye kiya gaya hai ke Allah ko maloom ho jaye ke kaun usko dekhe bagair uski aur uske rasoolon ki madad karta hai. Yaqeenan Allah badi quwwat wala aur zabardast hai"
  57,26,Humne Nooh aur Ibrahim ko bheja aur un dono ki nasal mein nabuwat aur kitaab rakh di phir unki aulad mein se kisi ne hidayat ikhtiyar ki aur bahut se faasiq ho gaye
  57,27,"Unke baad humne pai dar pai (succession) apne Rasool bheje, aur in sabke baad Isa ibn-e-Maryam ko maboos kiya aur usko Injil ata ki, aur jin logon ne uski pairvi ikhtiyar ki unke dilon mein humne taras (tenderness ) aur reham daal diya. Aur rahbaniyat (monasticism) unhon ne khud ijaad karli, humne usey unpar farz nahin kiya tha. Magar Allah ki khushnudi ki talab mein unhon ne aap hi yeh bidaat nikali aur phir iski pabandi karne ka jo haqq tha usey ada na kiya. Unmein se jo log iman laye huye thay unka ajr humne unko ata kiya, magar unmein se aksar log faasiq hain"
  57,28,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, Allah se daro aur uske Rasool par iman lao. Allah tumhein apni Rehmat ka dohra hissa ata farmyega aur tumhein wahi noor bakhshega jiski roshni mein tum chaloge, aur tumhare kasoor maaf kardega.Allah bada maaf karne wala aur meharbaan hai"
  57,29,"(Tumko yeh rawish ikhtiyar karni chahiye) taa-ke ehle kitaab ko maalom ho jaye ke Allah ke fazal par unka koi ijara (control/ikhtiyar) nahin hai, aur yeh ke Allah ka fazal uske apne hi haath mein hai, Jisey chahta hai ata farmata hai. Aur woh badey fazal(bounty) wala hai"
  58,1,Allah ne sun li us aurat ki baat jo apne shohar kay maamle mein tumse takrar kar rahi hai aur Allah se faryaad kiye jati hai.Allah tum dono ki guftagu sun raha hai. Woh sab kuch sunnay aur dekhne wala hai
  58,2,Tum mein se jo log apni biwiyon se zihar (divorce their wives by declaring them to be their mothers) karte hai unki biwiyan unki maayein (mothers) nahin hain. Unki maayein to wahi hai jinhon ne unko jana hai. Yeh log ek sakht napasandeeda aur jhooti baat kehte hain. Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah bada maaf karne wala aur darguzar farmane wala hai
  58,3,"Jo log apni biwiyon se zihar karein phir apni us baat se ruju (to go back) karein jo unhon ne kahi thi, to qabl iske ke dono ek dursre ko haath lagayein ,ek ghulaam azaad karna hoga. Issey tumko naseehat ki jati hai, Aur jo kuch tum karte ho Allah ussey bakhabar hai"
  58,4,"Aur jo shaks ghulaam na paye woh do mahine ke pai dar pai (consecutively) rozey rakkhey qabl iske ke dono ek dusre ko haath lagayein aur jo ispar bhi qadir na ho woh 60 miskeeno ko khana khilaye. Yeh hukum isliye diya ja raha hai ke tum Allah aur uske Rasool par iman lao. Yeh Allah ki mukarrar ki hui hadein (bounds) hain, aur kafiron ke liye dardnaak saza hai"
  58,5,"Jo log Allah ki aur uske Rasool ki mukhalifat karte hain woh usi tarah zaleel-o-khwar kardiye jayenge jis tarah unsey pehle ke log zaleel-o-khwar kiye ja chuke hain. Humne saaf saaf ayaat nazil kardi hain , aur kafiron ke liye zillat ka azaab hai"
  58,6,Us din (yeh zillat ka azaab hona hai) jab Allah in sabko phir se zinda karke uthayega aur inhein bata dega ke woh kya kuch karke aaye hain. Woh bhool gaye hain magar Allah ne in sabka kiya dhara gin gin kar mehfooz kar rakkha hai. Aur Allah ek ek cheez par shahid (witness) hai
  58,7,"Kya tumko khabar nahin hai ke zameen aur aasmano ki har cheez ka Allah ko ilm hai? Kabhi aisa nahin hota ke teen aadmiyon mein koi sargoshi(whispering) ho aur unke darmiyan chautha (fourth) Allah na ho, ya paanch aadmiyon mein sargoshi ho aur unke andar chatta (sixth) Allah na ho, khufiya baat karne wala khwa issey kam ho ya zyada jahan kahin bhi woh ho, Allah unke saath hota hai. Phir qayamat ke roz woh unko bata dega ke unhon ne kya kuch kiya hai. Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
  58,8,"Kya tumne dekha nahin un logon ko jinhein sargoshiyan karne se mana kardiya gaya tha phir bhi woh wahi harkat kiye jatay hain jissey unhein mana kiya gaya tha? Yeh log chup chup kar aapas mein gunaah aur zyadati aur Rasool ki nafarmani ki baatein karte hain. Aur jab tumhare paas aatey hain to tumhein us tarikey se salaam karte hain jis taraah Allah ne tumpar salaam nahin kiya hai, aur apne dilon mein kehte hain ke “hamari in baaton par Allah humein azaab kyun nahin deta”. Unke liye jahannum hi kaafi hai, usi ka woh indhan (fuel) banengey, bada hi bura anjaam hai unka"
  58,9,"Aye logon jo iman laye ho jab tum apas mein poshida baat karo to gunaah aur zyadati aur Rasool ki nafarmani ki baatein nahin, balkey neki aur taqwa ki baatein karo aur us khuda se darte raho jiske huzoor tumhein hashr mein pesh hona hai"
  58,10,"Kana-phusi (Whispering) to ek shaytani kaam hai, aur woh isliye ki jati hai ke iman laney waley log ussey ranjeedha hon, halanke bay-izan-e-khuda (except by Allahs will) woh unhein kuch bhi nuksaan nahin pahuncha sakti, aur momino ko Allah hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye"
  58,11,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, jab tumse kaha jaye ke apni majlison mein kushadgi paida karo(Make room) to jagah kushada kardiya karo, Allah tumhein kushadgi bakhshega. Aur jab tumse kaha jaye ke uth jao to uth jaya karo, tum mein se jo log iman rakhne waley hain aur jinko ilm bakhsha gaya hai, Allah unko buland darje ata farmayega. Aur jo kuch tum karte ho Allah ko uski khabar hai"
  58,12,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, jab tum Rasool se takhliye (privacy) mein baat karo to baat karne se pehle kuch sadaqa do. Yeh tumhare liye behtar aur pakeeza-tarr hai. Albatta agar tum sadaqa dene ke liye kuch na pao to Allah Gafoor-o-Raheem hai"
  58,13,"Kya tum darr gaye is baat se ke takhliye (privacy) mein guftagu karne se pehle tumhein sadaqaat dene hongey? Accha, agar tum aisa na karo aur Allah ne tumko issey maaf kardiya to namaz qayam karte raho, zakaat dete raho aur Allah aur uske Rasool ki itaat karte raho. Tum jo kuch karte ho Allah ussey bakhabar hai"
  58,14,"Kya tumne dekha nahin un logon ko jinhon ne dost banaya hai ek aisey giroh (people) ko jo Allah ka magzoob (gazabnaak/ Wrath) hai? Woh na tumhare hain na unke, aur wo jaan boojh kar jhooti baat par kasamein khate hain"
  58,15,Allah Ne unke liye sakht azaab muhayya kar rakkha hai. Badey hi burey kartoot hain jo woh kar rahey hain
  58,16,Unhon ne apni kasamo ko dhaal bana rakkha hai jiski aadh(shield) mein woh Allah ki raah se logon ko roakte hain. Ispar unke liye zillat ka azaab hai
  58,17,"Allah se bachane ke liye na unke maal kuch kaam aayege na unki aulad .Woh dozakh ke yaar hain, usi mein woh hamesha rahenge"
  58,18,"Jis roz Allah un sab ko uthayega, woh uske saamne bhi usi taraah kasamein kahyenge jis tarah tumhare saamne khate hain, aur apne nazdeek yeh samajhenge ke issey unka kuch kaam ban jayega. Khoob jaan lo woh parle daraje ke jhootey hain"
  58,19,"Shaytaan unpar musallat ho chuka hai aur usne khuda ki yaad unke dil se bhula di hai.Woh shaytaan ki party ke log hain. Khabardaar ho, shaytaan ki party waley hi khasarey mein rehne waley hai"
  58,20,Yaqeenan zaleel tareen makhlooqat mein se hain woh log jo Allah aur uske Rasool ka muqabla karte hain
  58,21,Allah ne likh diya hai ke main aur mere Rasool ghalib hokar rahenge. Fil waqey Allah zabardast aur zoarawar (most strong) hai
  58,22,"Tum kabhi yeh na paogey ke jo log Allah aur aakhirat par iman rakhne waley hain woh un logon se muhabbat karte hon jinhon ne Allah aur uske rasool ki mukhalifat ki hai , khwa woh unke baap hoon, ya unke betay, ya unke bhai ya unke ehle khandaan. Yeh woh log hain jinke dilon mein Allah ne iman sabt (inscribe/written) kar diya hai aur apni taraf se ek rooh ata karke unko quwwat bakshi hai, Woh unko aisey jannaton mein daakhil karega jinke nichey nehrein behti hongi. Unmein woh hamesha rahenge. Allah un se razi (pleased) hua aur woh Allah se razi huey.Woh Allah ki party ke log hain. Khabardar raho, Allah ki party waley hi falaah paney waley hain"
  59,1,"Allah hi ki tasbeeh ki hai har us cheez ne jo aasmano aur zameen mein hai, aur wahi ghalib aur hakeem hai"
  59,2,"Wahi hai jisne ehle kitaab kafiron ko pehle hi hamle mein unke gharon se nikaal bahar kiya.Tumhein hargiz yeh gumaan na tha ke woh nikal jayenge aur woh bhi yeh samjhe baitey thay ke unki gadiyan (fortresses) unhein Allah se bacha lengi.Magar Allah aisey rukh se un par aaya jidhar unka khayal bhi na gaya tha. Usney unke dilon mein roab (terror) daal diya, nateeja yeh hua ke woh khud apne haathon se bhi apne gharon ko barbaad kar rahey thay aur momino ke haathon bhi barbaad karwa rahey thay. Pas ibrat haasil karo aey deedha-e-beena (perceptive eyes) rakhne walon"
  59,3,Agar Allah ne unke haqq mein jila watani (banishment) na likh di hoti to duniya hi mein woh unhein azaab de daalta. Aur aakhirat mein to unke liye dozakh ka azaab hai hi
  59,4,Yeh sab kuch isliye hua ke unhon ne Allah aur uske Rasool ka muqabla kiya. Aur jo bhi Allah ka muqabla karey Allah usko saza dene mein bahut sakht hai
  59,5,"Tum logon ne khajooron (dates) ke jo darakht kaate ya jinko apne jadhon (roots) par khada rehne diya, yeh sab Allah hi ke izan se tha aur (Allah ne yeh izan isliye diya) taa-ke faasiqon ko zaleel-o-khaar karey"
  59,6,"Aur jo maal Allah ne unke kabze se nikal kar apne Rasool ki taraf palta diye, woh aisey maal nahin hai jinpar tumne apne ghodey (horses) aur ount (camels) daudaye hon. Balke Allah apne Rasoolon ko jispar chahta hai tasallut (authority/galaba) ata farma deta hai. Aur Allah har cheez par qadir hai"
  59,7,"Jo kuch bhi Allah in bastiyon ke logon se apne Rasool ki tarf palta de woh Allah , aur Rasool, aur rishtedaron , aur yatama (orphans), aur masakeen, aur musafiron, ke liye hai taa-ke woh tumhare maaldaaron hi ke darmiyan gardish na karta rahey. Jo kuch Rasool tumhein de woh lelo aur jis cheez se woh tum ko roak dey ussey ruk jao. Allah se daro, Allah sakht saza dene wala hai"
  59,8,(Neiz woh maal) un gareeb muhajireen ke liye hai jo apne gharon aur jaidaadon se nikaal bahar kiye gaye hain. Yeh log Allah ka fazal aur uski khushnudi chahte hain aur Allah aur uske Rasool ki himayat par qamar-basta rehte hai. Yahi raast baaz ( truthful ) log hain
  59,9,"(Aur woh un logon ke liye bhi hai) jo in muhajireen ki aamad se pehle hi iman laa kar daar-ul-hijrat [abode (of Hijrah)] mein muqeem thay. Yeh un logon se muhabbat karte hain jo hijrat karke inke paas aaye hain aur jo kuch bhi unko de diya jaye uski koi haajat tak yeh apne dilon mein mehsoos nahin karte aur apni zaat par dusron ko tarjeeh dete hain, khwa apni jagah khud mohtaj hon. Haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log apne dil ki tangi se bacha liye gaye wahi falaah paney waley hain"
  59,10,"(Aur woh un logon ke liye bhi hai) jo un logon ke baad aaye hain, jo kehte hain ke “Aey hamare Rubb, humein aur hamare un sab bhaiyon ko baksh de jo humse pehle iman laye hain aur hamare dilon mein ehle iman ke liye koi bugz (rancour) na rakh. Aey hamare Rubb, tu bada meharbaan aur raheem hai”"
  59,11,"Tumne dekha nahin un logon ko jinhon ne munafiqat (hypocrisy) ki rawish ikhtiyar ki hai? Yeh apne kafir ehle kitaab bhaiyon se kehte hain \"agar tumhein nikala gaya to hum tumhare saath niklenge, aur tumhare maamle mein hum kisi ki baat hargiz na manenge, aur agar tumse jung ki gayi to hum tumhari madad karenge\" magar Allah gawah hai ke yeh log qataii jhootey hain"
  59,12,"Agar woh nikale gaye to yeh unke saath hargiz na niklenge, aur agar unse jung ki gayi to yeh unki hargiz madad na karenge, aur agar yeh unki madad karein bhi to peet phair jayenge aur phir kahin se koi madad na payenge"
  59,13,"Inke dilon mein Allah se badh kar tumhara khauf hai, isliye ke yeh aisey log hain jo samajh boojh nahin rakhte"
  59,14,"Yeh kabhi ikatthey hokar ( khule maidan mein ) tumhara muqabla na karenge, ladenge bhi to qila-band bastiyon ( fortified townships) mein baith kar ya deewaron ke peechay chup kar. Yeh aapas ki mukhalifat mein baday sakht hain. Tum unhein ikhatta samajte ho magar inke dil ek dusre se phatey huey hain. Inka yeh haal isliye hai ke yeh be aqal log hain"
  59,15,Yeh unhi logon ke manind hain jo insey thodi hi muddat pehle apne kiye ka maza chakh chuke hain aur inke liye dardnaak azaab hai
  59,16,"Inki misal shaytaan ki si hai ke pehle woh insan se kehta hai kufr kar, aur jab Insan kufr kar baithta hai to woh kehta hai main tujhse bari-uz-zimma hoon, mujhey to Allah Rabb-ul-aalameen se darr lagta hai"
  59,17,"Phir dono ka anjaam yeh hona hai ke hamesha ke liye jahannum mein jayein, aur zaalimon ki yahi jaza hai"
  59,18,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, Allah se daro, Aur har shaks yeh dekhe ke usne kal ke liye kya samaan kiya hai. Allah se darte raho, Allah yaqeenan tumhare un sab aamaal se ba-khabar hai jo tum karte ho"
  59,19,Un logon ki taraah na ho jao jo Allah ko bhool gaye to Allah ne unhein khud apna nafs bhula diya. yahi log faasiq hain
  59,20,Dozakh mein jaane wale aur jannat mein jaane wale kabhi yaksan nahin ho sakte. Jannat mein janey waley hi asal mein kamiyaab hain
  59,21,"Agar humne yeh Quran kisi pahad(mountain) par bhi utaar diya hota to tum dekhte ke woh Allah ke khauff se daba jaa raha hai, aur phata padta hai. Yeh misalein hum logon ke saamne isliye bayaan karte hain ke woh (apne halaat par) gaur karein"
  59,22,"Woh Allah hi hai jiske siwa koi maabood nahin, gayab aur zaahir har cheez ka jaanne wala, wahi Rehman aur Raheem hai"
  59,23,"Woh Allah hi hai jiske siwa koi maabood nahin woh Badshah hai, nihayat muqaddas , sarasar salamati (all-peace), aman dene wala( Giver of security), nigehbaan, sab par ghalib, apna hukum ba-zoar naafiz karne wala, aur bada hi hokar rehne wala. Paak hai Allah us shirk se jo log kar rahey hain"
  59,24,"Woh Allah hi hai, jo takhleeq( creation) ka mansuba(plan) banane wala, aur usko nafiz karne wala, aur uske mutabik surat-gari (fashioner) karne wala hai. Uske liye behtareen naam hain. Har cheez jo aasmano aur zameen mein hai uski tasbeeh kar rahi hai, aur woh zabardast aur Hakeem hai"
  60,1,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, agar tum meri raah mein jihad karne ke liye aur meri raza-joyi ki khatir (watan chodh kar gharon se) nikle ho to mere aur apne dushmano ko dost na banao. Tum unke saath dosti ki tarah(befriend) dalte ho, halaanke jo haqq tumhare paas aaya hai usko maanne se woh inkar kar chuke hain. Aur unki ravish yeh hai ke Rasool ko aur khud tumko sirf is kasoor par jila-watan (expel) karte hain ke tum apne Rubb, Allah par iman laye ho. Tum chupa kar unko dostana paighaam bhejte ho, halaanke jo kuch tum chupa kar karte ho aur jo elania (openly) karte ho, har cheez ko mai khoob janta hoon. Jo shaks bhi tum mein se aisa karey woh yaqeenan raah-e-raast se bhatak gaya"
  60,2,"Unka rawayya to yeh hai ke agar tumpar qaabu paa jayein to tumhare saath dushmani karein aur haath aur zuban se tumhein azar (hurt) dein, woh to yeh chahte hain ke tum kisi tarah kafir ho jao"
  60,3,Qayamat ke din na tumhari rishtedarian kisi kaam aayengi na tumhari aulad. Us roz Allah tumhare darmiyan judaai daal dega. Aur wahi tumhare aamaal ka dekhne wala hai
  60,4,"Tum logon ke liye Ibrahim aur uske saathiyon mein ek accha namuna hai ke unhon ne apni qaum se saaf kehdiya “hum tumse aur tumhare in maboodon (deities) se jinko tum khuda ko chodh kar poojhte ho qataii bezaar hain. Humne tumse kufr kiya aur hamare aur tumhare darmiyan hamesha ke liye adawat hogayi aur bair padh gaya (enmity and hatred) jabtak tum Allah wahid par iman na lao”. Magar Ibrahim ka apne baap se yeh kehna (issey mustasna hai) ke “ Main aapke liye magfirat ki darkhwast zaroor karunga, aur Allah se aap ke liye kuch haasil kar lena mere bas mein nahin hai”. (Aur Ibrahim va ashaab-e-Ibrahim ki dua yeh thi ke) “Aey hamare Rubb, tere hi upar humne bharosa kiya aur teri hi taraf humne ruju (turn) karliya aur tere hi huzoor humein palatna hai"
  60,5,"Aey hamare Rubb, humein kafiron ke liye fitna (trial/test) na bana de aur aey hamare Rubb, hamare kasooron se darguzar farma. Beshak tu hi zabardast (mighty) aur daana(wise) hai"
  60,6,Inhi logon ke tarz-e-amal mein tumhare liye aur har us shaks ke liye accha namuna (example) hai jo Allah aur roz-e-aakhir ka umeedwar ho. Issey koi munharif ho (turns away) to Allah be niyaz (All-Sufficient) aur apni zaat mein aap mahmood hai
  60,7,Baeed nahin ke Allah kabhi tumhare aur un logon ke darmiyaan mohabbat daal de jinse aaj tumne dushmani mol li hai. Allah badi qudrat rakhta hai aur woh gafoor-o-raheem hai
  60,8,Allah tumhein is baat se nahin roakta ke tum un logon ke saath neki aur insaaf ka bartaao karo jinhon ne deen ke maamle mein tumse jung nahin ki hai aur tumhein tumhare gharon se nahin nikala hai. Allah insaaf karne walon ko pasand karta hai
  60,9,Woh tumhein jis baat se roakta hai woh to yeh hai ke tum un logon se dosti karo jinhon ne tumse deen ke maamle mein jung ki hai aur tumhein tumhare gharon se nikala hai aur tumhare ikhraaj (expulsion) mein ek dusre ki madad ki hai. Unse jo log dosti karein wahi zaalim hain
  60,10,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, jab momin auratein hijrat karke tumhare paas aayein to (unke momin honay ki) jaanch padtaal karlo. Aur unke iman ki haqeeqat Allah hi behtar janta hai. Phir jab tumhein maloom ho jaye ke woh momin hain to unhein kuffar ki taraf wapas na karo. Na woh kuffar ke liye halal hain aur na kuffar unke liye halal. Unke kafir shoharon ne jo mehar unko diye thay woh unhein pher do aur unsey nikah kar lene par tumse koi gunaah nahin jabke tum unke mehar unko ada kardo. Aur tum khud bhi kafir auraton ko apne nikah mein na roakey raho, jo mehar tumne apni kafir biwiyon ko diye thay woh tum wapas maang lo aur jo mehar kafiron ne apni musalmaan biwiyon ko diye thay unhein woh wapas maang lein. Yeh Allah ka hukum hai, woh tumhare darmiyaan faisla karta hai aur Allah Aleem-o-Hakeem (all knowing-most wise) hai"
  60,11,Aur agar tumhari kafir biwiyon ke meharon mein se kuch tumhein kuffar se wapas na miley aur phir tumhari naubat aaye to jin logon ki biwiyan udhar reh gayi hain unko itni rakam ada kardo jo unke diye huey meharon ke barabar ho. Aur us khuda se darte raho jispar tum iman laye ho
  60,12,"Aey Nabi, Jab tumhare paas momin auratein bayt (pledge) karne ke liye aayein aur is baat ka ahad karein ke woh Allah ke saath kisi cheez ko shareek na karengi, chori na karengi, zina na karengi, apni aulad ko qatal na karengi, apne haath paaon ke aage koi bohtan (calumny) ghad kar na layengi, Aur kisi amr-e-maaroof (anything known to be good) mein tumhari nafarmani na karengi, to unse bayt lelo aur unke haqq mein Allah se dua-e-magfirat karo. Yaqeenan Allah darguzar(maaf) farmane wala aur Reham karne wala hai"
  60,13,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, un logon ko dost na banao jinpar Allah ne gazab farmaya hai, Jo aakhirat se usi tarah mayous hain jis tarah kabaron mein padey huey kafir mayous hain"
  61,1,"Allah ki tasbeeh ki hai har us cheez ne jo aasmano aur zameen mein hai, Aur woh ghalib (Mighty) aur Hakeem (wise) hai"
  61,2,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, tum kyun woh baat kehte ho jo karte nahin ho"
  61,3,Allah ke nazdeek yeh sakht na pasandeeda harakat hai ke tum kaho woh baat jo karte nahin
  61,4,Allah ko to pasand woh log hain jo uski raah mein is tarah saff-basta(row) hokar ladte hain goya ke woh ek sisa pilayi hui deewar hain
  61,5,"Aur yaad karo Moosa ki woh baat jo usne apni qaum se kahi thi “Aey meri qaum ke logon, tum kyun mujhey aziyat (torment /harm) dete ho halaanke tum khoob jaante ho ke main tumhari taraf Allah ka bheja hua Rasool hoon? Phir jab unhon ne tedh ikhtiyar ki (deviated) to Allah ne unke dil tedhey (deviant) kardiye, Allah faasiqon ko hidayat nahin deta"
  61,6,"Aur yaad karo Isa ibn-e-Maryam ki woh baat jo usne kahi thi ke “Aey bani Israel, main tumhari taraf Allah ka bheja hua Rasool hoon, Tasdeeq (verify/confirm) karne wala hoon us Taurat ki jo mujhse pehle aayi hui maujood hai, aur basharat (khushkhabri) dene wala hoon ek rasool ki jo mere baad aayega jiska naam Ahmed hoga. Magar jab woh unke paas khuli khuli nishaniyan lekar aaya to unhon ne kaha yeh to sareeh dhoka hai"
  61,7,Ab bhala us shaks se bada zaalim aur kaun hoga jo Allah par jhutey bohtan bandhey halaanke usey Islam (Allah ke aagey sar-e-itaat jhuka deney) ki dawat di ja rahi ho? Aisey zaalimon ko Allah hidayat nahin diya karta
  61,8,"Yeh log apni mooh ki phoonkon (blows) se Allah ke noor ko bujhana chahte hain, Aur Allah ka faisla yeh hai ke wo apne noor ko poora phayla kar rahega khwa kaafiron ko yeh kitna hi nagawar ho"
  61,9,Wahi to hai jisne apne Rasool ko hidayat aur deen-e-haqq ke saath bheja hai taa-ke usey poorey ke poorey deen par ghalib karde khwa mushrikeen ko yeh kitna hi nagawar ho
  61,10,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, main bataoon tumko wo tijarat jo tumhein azaab-e-aleem se bacha de"
  61,11,"Iman lao Allah aur uske Rasool par, Aur jihad karo Allah ki raah mein apne maalon se aur apni jaano se, yahi tumhare liye behtar hai agar tum jaano"
  61,12,"Allah tumhare gunaah maaf kardega, aur tumko aisey baaghon mein daakhil karega jinke nichey nehrein behti hongi, aur abadi (eternal) qayaam ki jannaton mein behtareen ghar tumhein ata farmaeyga. Yeh hai badi kamiyabi"
  61,13,"Aur woh dusri cheez jo tum chahte ho woh bhi tumhein dega, Allah ki taraf se nusrat (victory) aur kareeb hi mein hasil ho janey wali fatah. Aey Nabi ehle iman ko iski basharat de do"
  61,14,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, Allah ke madadgaar bano , jis tarah Isa ibn-e-Maryam ne hawariyon (disciples) ko khitaab karke kaha tha “Kaun hai Allah ki taraf (bulane) mein mera madadgaar”. Aur hawariyon (disciples) ne jawab diya tha : “hum hai Allah ke madadgaar”. Us waqt bani Israel ka ek giroh iman laya aur dusre giroh ne inkar kiya. Phir humne iman laney walon ki unke dushmano ke muqable mein taeed ki (aided) aur wahi ghalib hokar rahey"
  62,1,"Allah ki tasbeeh kar rahi hai har woh cheez jo aasmano mein hai aur har wo cheez jo zameen mein hai, baadshah hai,Quddus(holy) hai,Zabardast aur Hakeem(wise) hai"
  62,2,"Wahi hai jisne ummiyon (gentiles/unlettered) ke andar ek Rasool khud unhi mein se uthaya, jo unhein uski ayaat sunata hai, unki zindagi sanwarta hai,aur unko kitaab aur hikmat ki taleem deta hai, halaanke issey pehle woh khuli gumraahi me padey huey thay"
  62,3,Aur (is Rasool ki beasat) un dusre logon ke liye bhi hai jo abhi unse nahi miley hain
  62,4,Allah Zabardast aur Hakeem hai yeh uska fazal hai jisey chahta hai deta ha. Aur woh bada fazal farmane wala hai
  62,5,"Jin logon ko Taurat ka hamil (charge) banaya gaya tha magar unhon ne uska baar na uthaya, unki misaal us gadhey(donkey) ki si hai jispar kitaabein laadi hui hon. Issey bhi zyada buri misaal hai un logon ki jinhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko jhutla diya hai. Aisey zaalimon ko Allah hidayat nahi diya karta"
  62,6,"Insey kaho, “aey logo jo yahudi ban gaye ho, agar tumhein yeh ghamand (arrogance) hai ke baqi sab logon ko chodh kar bas tum hi Allah ke chahite (favourites) ho to maut ki tamanna karo agar tum apne is zaam (claim) mein sachche ho"
  62,7,lekin yeh hargiz iski tamanna na karenge apne kartooton ki wajah se jo ye kar chuke hain. Aur Allah in zalimon ko khoob jaanta hai
  62,8,"Insey kaho , “jis maut se tum bhaagte ho wo to tumhein aakar rahegi. Phir tum uske saamne pesh kiye jaogey jo poshida (hidden) aur zaahir ka jaanne wala hai. Aur woh tumhein bata dega ke tum kya kuch karte rahey ho"
  62,9,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, jab pukara jaye namaz ke liye jumaa ke din to Allah ke zikr ki taraf daudo aur khareed-o-farokht chodh do. Yeh tumhare liye zyada bethar hai agar tum jaano"
  62,10,"Phir jab namaz poori ho jaye to zameen mein phayl jao aur Allah ka fazl talash karo aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad karte raho, shayad ke tumhein falaah (kamiyabi/prosperity) naseeb ho jaye"
  62,11,"Aur jab unhon ne tijarat (business) aur khel tamasha hote dekha to uski taraf lapak gaye aur tumhein khada chodh diya. Insey kaho, jo kuch Allah ke paas hai wo khel tamashey aur tijarat se behtar hai aur Allah sabse behtar rizq (sustenance) dene wala hai"
  63,1,"Aey Nabi, jab yeh munafiq (hypocrites) tumhare paas aate hain to kehte hain “hum gawahi dete hain ke aap yaqeenan Allah ke Rasool hain, “haan, Allah janta hai ke tum zaroor uske Rasool ho, magar Allah gawahi deta hai ke yeh munafiq qataii jhootey hain"
  63,2,Inhon ne apni kasamo ko dhaal bana rakkha hai aur is tarah yeh Allah ke raste se khud rukte aur duniya ko roakte hain. Kaisi buri harkatein hain jo yeh log kar rahey hain
  63,3,"Yeh sab kuch is wajah se hai ke in logon ne Imaan la kar phir kufr kiya is liye inke dilon par mohar laga di gayi, ab yeh kuch nahin samajhte"
  63,4,"Inhein dekho to inke jussey(jism/bodies) tumhein badey shaandaar nazar aayein bolein to tum inki batein sunte reh jao, magar asal mein yeh goya lakhdi ke kunde hain(beams of timber) jo deewar ke saath chun kar rakh diye gaye hon. Har zoar ki aawaz ko yeh apne khilaf samajhte hain. Yeh pakke dushman hain insey bachh kar raho. Allah ki maar inpar yeh kidhar ultey phiraye ja rahe hain"
  63,5,"Aur jab inse kaha jata hai ke aao taa-ke Allah ka Rasool tumhare liye magfirat ki dua karey, To sar jhatakte hain aur tum dekhte ho ke woh bade ghamand ke saath aane se rukte hai"
  63,6,"Aey Nabi, tum chahe inke liye magfirat ki dua karo ya na karo, inke liye yaksan hai , Allah hargiz inhein maaf nahin karega. Allah faasik logon(transgressing folk) ko hargiz hidayat nahin deta"
  63,7,"Yeh wahi log hain jo kehte hain ke Rasool ke saathiyon par kharch karna bandh kardo taa-ke yeh muntashir ho jayein. Halaanke zameen aur aasmaano ke khazano ka maalik Allah hi hai, magar yeh munafik samajhte nahin hain"
  63,8,"Yeh kehte hain ke hum medina wapas pahunch jayein to jo izzat wala hai woh zaleel ko wahan se nikal bahar karega. Halaanke izzat to Allah aur uske Rasool aur momineen ke liye hai, magar yeh munafiq jante nahin hain"
  63,9,"Aey logon jo imaan laye ho , tumhare maal aur tumhari auladein tumko Allah ki yaad se gaafil na kardein. Jo log aisa karein wahi khasare (nuqsan /loss) mein rehne waley hain"
  63,10,"Jo rizq humne tumhein diya hai usmein se kharch karo qabl iske ke tum mein se kisi ki maut ka waqt aa jaye aur us waqt woh kahey \"Aey mere Rubb, kyun na tu nay mujhey thodi si mahulat aur de di ke main sadaqa deta aur saleh logon mein shamil ho jata”"
  63,11,"Halanke jab kisi ki mahulat-e-amal puri hone ka waqt aa jata hai to Allah us ko hargiz mazeed mahulat nahin deta, aur jo kuch tum karte ho, Allah usse bakhabar hai"
  64,1,Allah ki tasbeeh kar rahi hai har woh cheez jo aasmano mein hai aur har woh cheez jo zameen mein hai usi ki baadshahi hai aur usi ke liye tareef hai aur woh har cheez par qadir hai
  64,2,"Wahi hai jisne tumko paida kiya, phir tum mein se koi kafir hai aur koi momin. Aur Allah woh sab kuch dekh raha hai jo tum karte ho"
  64,3,"Usne zameen aur aasmano ko barhaqq paida kiya hai, aur tumhari surat banayi aur badi umdah (excellent) banayi hai, aur usi ki taraf aakhir-e-kaar tumhein palatna hai"
  64,4,Zameen aur aasmano ki har cheez ka usey ilm hai jo kuch tum chupatey ho aur jo kuch tum zaahir karte ho sab us ko maloom hai. Aur woh dilon ka haal tak jaanta hai
  64,5,kya tumhein un logon ki koi khabar nahi pahunchi jinhon ne issey pehle kufar kiya aur phir apni shamat-e-aamaal (evil consequence) ka maza chakkh liya? aur aagey unke liye ek dardnaak azaab hai
  64,6,"Is anjaam ke mustahiq woh is liye huey ke unke paas unke Rasool khuli khuli daleelein (clear signs) aur nishaniyan lekar aate rahey, magar unhon ne kaha\" kya Insan humein hadayat deinge ?\" Is tarah unhon ne maanne se inkaar kardiya aur mooh pheir liya. Tab Allah bhi unsey be-parwa ho gaya aur Allah to hai hi be niyaz aur apni zaat mein aap Mahmood (Praiseworthy)"
  64,7,"Munkireen ne badey dawey se kaha hai ke woh marne ke baad hargiz dobara na uthaye jayenge. Insey kaho\" nahin, mere Rubb ki kasam tum zaroor uthaye jaogey, phir zaroor tumhein bataya jayega ke tumne (duniya mein) kya kuch kiya hai aur aisa karna Allah ke liye bahut aasaan hai"
  64,8,"Pas iman lao Allah par, aur uske Rasool par, aur us roshni par jo humne nazil ki hai. Jo kuch tum karte ho Allah usse bakhabar hai"
  64,9,"(Iska pata tumhein us roz chal jayega ) jab ijtima (will assemble you )ke din woh tum sabko ikattha karega. Woh din hoga ek dusre ke muqable mein logon ki haar jeet ka. Jo Allah par iman laya hai aur neik amal karta hai, Allah uske gunah jhaad dega aur usey aisi jannaton mein daakhil karega jinke nichey nehrein behti hongi. Yeh log hamesha hamesha inmein rahenge. Yahi badi kamiyabi hai"
  64,10,"Aur jin logon ne kufr kiya hai aur hamari aayaat ko jhutlaya hai woh dozakh ke bashindey(inmates ) honge, jismein woh hamesha rahenge. Aur woh badhtareen thikana hai"
  64,11,Koi museebat kabhi nahi aati magar Allah ke izan(Allah’s leave) hi se aati hai. Jo shakhs Allah par iman rakhta ho Allah uske dil ko hidayat bakshta hai. Aur Allah ko har cheez ka ilm hai
  64,12,Allah ki itaat karo aur Rasool ki itaat karo lekin agar tum itaat se mooh moadtey ho to hamarey Rasool par saaf saaf haqq pahuncha dene ke siwa koi zimmedari nahin hai
  64,13,"Allah woh hai jiske siwa koi khuda nahin, lihaza iman laney walon ko Allah hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye"
  64,14,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, tumhari biwiyon aur tumhari aulad mein se baaz tumhare dushman hain, Inse hoshiyar raho. Aur agar tum Affu-o-darguzar(forgive and overlook) se kaam lo aur maaf kardo to Allah gafoor-o-Raheem hai"
  64,15,"Tumhare maal aur tumhari aulad to ek aazmaish hai, aur Allah hi hai jiske paas bada ajar hai"
  64,16,"lihaza jahan tak tumhare bas mein ho Allah se darte raho, aur suno aur itaat karo, aur apne maal kharch karo, yeh tumhare hi liye behtar hai. Jo apne dil ki tanggi se mehfooz reh gaye bas wahi falaah paney waley hain"
  64,17,Agar tum Allah ko qarz-e-hasan do to woh tumhein kai guna (several fold) badha kar dega aur tumhare kasooron se dar guzar farmayega. Allah bada qadardaan aur burdbar (Most Forbearing) hai
  64,18,"Haazir aur gayab har cheez ko jaanta hai, zabardast (mighty) aur daana(Most Wise) hai"
  65,1,"Aey Nabi, jab tumlog auraton ko talaq do to unhein unki iddat (waiting-period) ke liye talaq diya karo aur iddat ke zamane ka theek theek shumar karo, aur Allah se daro jo tumhara Rubb hai (zamana-e-iddat mein) na tum unhein unke gharon se nikalo aur na woh khud nikle, illa yeh ke woh kisi sareeh burayi ki murtakib ho(manifestly evil deed). Yeh Allah ki muqarrar karda hadein hain, aur jo koi Allah ki hadon (bounds/limits) se tajauz karega woh apne upar khud zulm karega. Tum nahin jaante shayad iske baad Allah (muwafikat/reconciliation ki) koi surat paida karde"
  65,2,"Phir jab woh apni (iddat ki) muddat ke khaatmay par pahunchey to ya unhein bhale tarike se (apne nikah mein ) rok rakkho , ya bhale tarike par unse juda ho jao, aur do aisey aadmiyon ko gawah bana lo jo tum mein se sahib-e-adal hon, aur (aey gawah banne walon)gawahi theek theek Allah ke liye ada karo. Yeh baatein hain jinki tum logon ko nasihat ki jati hai, har us shaks ko jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par iman rakhta ho. Jo koi Allah se darte huey kaam karega Allah uske liye mushkilat se nikalne ka koi rasta paida kardega"
  65,3,"Aur usey aise raaste se rizq dega jidhar uska guman(imagination) bhi na jata ho. Jo Allah par bharosa karey uske liye woh kafi hai. Allah apna kaam pura karke rehta hai, Allah ne har cheez ke liye ek taqdeer muqarrar kar rakkhi hai"
  65,4,Aur tumhari auraton mein se jo haiz(menstruation) se mayous ho chuki hon unke maamle mein agar tum logon ko koi shak lahik hai to ( tumhe maloom ho ke ) unki iddat teen mahiney hai aur yahi hukum unka hai jinhein abhi haiz na aaya ho.Aur haamila(pregnant) aurton ki iddat ki hadd yeh hai ke unka waze hamal(delivery) ho jaye. Jo shakhs Allah se darey uske maamle mein woh sahulat paida kar deta hai
  65,5,Yeh Allah ka hukum hai jo usne tumhari taraf nazil kiya hai. Jo Allah se darega Allah uski buraiyon ko ussey door kardega aur usko bada ajar dega
  65,6,"Unko ( zamana-e-iddat mein ) usi jagah rakkho jahan tum rehtey ho, jaisi kuch bhi jagah tumhe muyassar ho, aur unhein tangg karne ke liye unko na satao. Aur agar woh haamila hon to unpar us waqt tak kharch karte raho jab tak unka waze hamal(delivered their burden) na ho jaye. Phir agar woh tumhare liye ( bachhey ko ) doodh pilayein to unki ujrat(recompense) unhein do, aur bhaley tareeqe se ( ujrat ka maamla) bahami guft-o-shaneed se tai karlo. Lekin agar tumne ( ujrat tai karne mein) ek dusrey ko tangg kiya to bachhey ko koi aur aurat doodh pila legi"
  65,7,"Khushaal aadmi apni khushaali ke mutabiq nafqa de, aur jisko rizq kam diya gaya ho woh usi maal mein se kharch karey jo Allah ne usey diya hai. Allah ne jisko jitna kuch diya hai ussey ziyada ka woh usey mukallaf(burden) nahi karta. Baeed(door) nahin ke Allah tangdasti ke baad farakh dasti bhi ataa farmade"
  65,8,Kitni hi bastiyan hain jinhon ne apne Rubb aur uske Rasoolon ke hukum se sartabi (rebel) ki to humne unsey sakht muhasiba kiya aur unko buri tarhaan saza di
  65,9,Unhon ne apne kiya ka maza chakkh liya aur unka anjaam-e-kaar ghaata hi ghaata(utter loss) hai
  65,10,Allah ne ( aakhirat mein ) unke liye sakht azaab muhaiyya kar rakha hai. Pas Allah se daro aey sahib-e-aqal logon jo imaan laaye ho. Allah ne tumhari taraf ek naseehat nazil kardi hai
  65,11,Ek aisa rasool jo tumko Allah ki saaf saaf hadaayat deney wali aayaat sunataa hai taa-ke imaan laane walon aur neik amal karne walon ko tarikiyon (darkness) se nikaal kar roshni mein le aaye. Jo koi Allah par imaan laaye aur neik amal karey Allah usey aisi jannaton mein daakhil karega jinke nichey nehrein behti hongi. Yeh log inmein hamesha hamesha rahenge. Allah ne aisey shakhs ke liye behtareen rizq rakkha hai
  65,12,"Allah woh hai jisne saat(seven) aasman banaye aur zameen ki qisam se bhi unhi ke manind (like them). Unke darmiyan hukum nazil hota rehta hai. (yeh baat tumhein isliye batayi jaa rahi hai ) taakey tum jaan lo ke Allah har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai, aur yeh ke Allah ka ilm har cheez par muheet (encompassing) hai"
  66,1,"Aey Nabi, Tum kyun us cheez ko haraam karte ho jo Allah ne tumhare liye halal ki hai? (kya is liye ke) tum apni biwiyon ki khushi chahte ho? Allah maaf karne wala aur Reham farmane wala hai"
  66,2,"Allah ne tum logon ke liye apni kasamo ki pabandi se nikalne ka tareeqa mukarrar kardiya hai Allah tumhara maula(guardian) hai aur wahi Aleem-o-Hakeem(All-Knowing, Most Wise) hai"
  66,3,"(Aur yeh maamla bhi kaabil-e-tawajjuh hai ke ) Nabi ne ek baat apni ek biwi se raaz mein kahi thi phir jab us biwi ne (kisi aur par) woh raaz zahir kardiya, aur Allah ne Nabi ko is (ifshaey raaz) ki ittila de di , to Nabi ne uspar kisi hadd tak (us biwi ko) khabardar kiya aur kisi hadd tak ussey dar-guzar kiya. Phir jab Nabi ne usey (ifshaey raaz ki ) yeh baat batayi to usne pucha aapko iski kisne khabar di? Nabi ne kaha “Mujhey usne khabar di jo sab kuch janta hai aur khoob bakhabar hai”"
  66,4,"Agar tum dono Allah se tauba karti ho (to yeh tumhare liye behtar hai) kyunke tumhare dil seedhi raah se hath gaye hain, aur agar Nabi ke muqable mein tumne baham jattah-bandi ki (support one another) to jaan rakkho ke Allah uska maula(Protector) hai aur uske baad Jibrael aur tammam saaleh ehle iman aur sab malaika uske saathi aur madadgaar hai"
  66,5,"Baeed (door) nahin ke agar Nabi tum sab biwiyon ko talaq dede to Allah usey aisi biwiyan tumhare badle mein ata farma de jo tumse behtar hon, sacchi musalman ,ba-iman, itaat guzar , tauba guzar, ibadat guzar, aur rozedar, khwa shohar deedha ho ya bakira (both previously wedded ones and virgins)"
  66,6,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho , bachao apne aap ko aur apne ehal-o-ayal ko (yourselves and your kindred) us aag se jis ka indhan (fuel) insaan aur patthar hongey, jispar nihayat tundh-khu (fierce) aur sakht-gir (stern) farishtey mukarrar hongey jo kabhi Allah ke hukum ki na farmani nahin karte aur jo hukm bhi unhein diya jata hai usey baja latey hain"
  66,7,"(Us waqt kaha jayega ke) aey kafiron aaj maazratein (excuses) pesh na karo, tumhein to waisa hi badla diya ja raha hai jaise tum amal kar rahey thay"
  66,8,"Aey logon jo iman laye ho, Allah se tauba karo, khalis tauba, baeed (door) nahin ke Allah tumhari buraiyan tumse dur karde aur tumhein aisi jannaton mein daakhil farmade jinke nichey nehrein beh rahi hongi, yeh woh din hoga jab Allah apne Nabi ko aur un logon ko jo uske saath iman laye hain ruswa na karega, unka noor unke aagey aagey aur unke dayein (right) jaanib daud raha hoga aur woh keh rahey hongey ke aey hamare Rubb, hamara noor hamare liye mukammal karde aur humse darguzar farma , tu har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  66,9,"Aey Nabi , kuffar aur munafikeen se jihad karo aur unke saath sakhti se pesh aao, unka thikana jahannum hai aur wo bahut bura thikana hai"
  66,10,"Allah kafiron ke maamle mein Nooh aur Lut ki biwiyon ko bataur-e-misal pesh karta hai, woh hamare do saleh bando ki zaujiyat (marriage/wedlock) mein thi, magar unhon ne apne in shoharon se khayanat (treachery) ki aur woh Allah ke muqable mein unke kuch bhi na kaam aa sakey. Dono se kehdiya gaya ke jao aag mein janey walon ke saath tum bhi chali jao"
  66,11,"Aur ehle iman ke maamle mein Allah Firoun ki biwi ki misal pesh karta hai jabke usne dua ki “Aey mere Rubb,mere liye apne haan jannat mein ek ghar bana de aur mujhey Firoun aur iske amal se bacha le aur zalim qaum se mujhko nijaat de.”"
  66,12,"Aur Imran ki beti Maryam ki misaal deta hai jisne apni sharmgaah ki hifazat ki thi, phir humne uske andar apni taraf se rooh phoonk di aur usne apne Rubb ke irshadaat aur uski kitabon ki tasdeeq ki aur woh itaat guzar (obedient) logon mein se thi"
  67,1,"Nihayat buzurg-o-bartar hai woh jiske haath mein qayinaat ki sultanat hai , aur woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  67,2,"Jisne maut aur zindagi ko ijaat kiya taa-ke tum logon ko aazma kar dekhey tum mein se kaun behtar amal karne wala hai, aur woh zabardast bhi hai aur darguzar farmane wala bhi"
  67,3,"Jisne teh-bar-teh saat (seven) aasman banaye tum Rehman ki takhleeq(creation) mein kisi kism ki be-rabti (incongruity) na paogey phir palat kar dekho, kahin tumhein koi khalal (flaw) nazar aata hai"
  67,4,Baar baar nigaah daudao tumhari nigaah thak kar na-murad palat aayegi
  67,5,Humne tumhare kareeb ke aasman ko azeem-o-shaan chiragon se aarasta (adorned /beautify) kiya hai aur unhein shayateen ko maar bhagane ka zariya bana diya hai. In shaytano ke liye bhadakti hui aag humne muhayya kar rakkhi hai
  67,6,Jin logon ne apne Rubb se kufr kiya hai unke liye jahannum ka azaab hai aur woh bahut hi bura thikana hai
  67,7,Jab woh usmein phenke jayenge to uske dhahadne (roar) ki haulnaak aawaz sunengey aur woh josh kha rahi hogi
  67,8,"Shiddat-e-gazab se phati jati hogi, har baar jab koi anbwah (multitude/group) us mein dala jayega uske kaarinde (keepers) un logon se puchenge “kya tumhare paas koi khabardaar karne wala nahin aaya tha?”"
  67,9,"Woh jawab denge “haan ,khabardaar karne wala hamare paas aaya tha,magar humne usey jhutla diya aur kaha Allah ne kuch bhi nazil nahin kiya hai, tum badi gumraahi mein padey huey ho”"
  67,10,Aur woh kahenge “kaash hum sunte ya samajhte to aaj is bhadakti hui aag ke sazawaron mein na shamil hotey”
  67,11,"Is tarah woh apne kasoor ka khud aitraaf (confess) kar lengey, laanat hai in dozakhiyon par"
  67,12,"Jo log be-dekhe apne Rubb se darte hai , yaqeenan unke liye magfirat hai aur bada ajar"
  67,13,Tum khwah chupke se baat karo ya unchi aawaz se (Allah ke liye yaksa hai) woh to dilon ka haal tak jaanta hai
  67,14,Kya wahi na jaanega jisne paida kiya hai? Halanke woh baareek-been aur bakhabar hai
  67,15,"Wahi to hai jisne tumhare liye zameen ko taabeh kar rakkha hai , chalo uski chaati par aur khao khuda ka rizq, usi ke huzoor tumhein dobara zinda ho kar jana hai"
  67,16,Kya tum issey be-khauf ho ke woh jo aasman mein hai tumhein zameen mein dhasa de aur yakayak yeh zameen jhakoley khane lagey (shake/rock violently)
  67,17,Kya tum issey be-khauf ho ke wo jo aasman mein hai tum par pathrao karne wali hawa bhej de? Phir tumhein maloom ho jayega ke meri tambeeh (warning) kaisi hoti hai
  67,18,Inse pehle guzre huey log jhutla chuke hain phir dekhlo ke meri giraft kaisi sakht thi
  67,19,Kya yeh log apne upar udney waley parindon ko par phaylaye aur sukedte nahin dekhte? Rehman ke siwa koi nahin jo inhein thamey huey ho. Wahi har cheez ka nigehbaan hai
  67,20,"Batao, aakhir woh kaunsa lashkar tumhare paas hai jo Rehman ke muqable mein tumhari madad kar sakta hai? Haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh mukireen dhoke mein padey huey hain"
  67,21,"Ya phir batao, kaun hai jo tumhein rizq de sakta hai agar Rehman apna rizq roak ley? Dar-asal yeh log sarkashi aur haqq se gurez par adey huey hai"
  67,22,"Bhala socho, jo shaks mooh aundhaey (grovelling) chal raha ho woh zyada sahih raah paney wala hai ya woh jo sar uthaye seedha ek hamwar sadak par chal raha ho"
  67,23,"Inse kaho Allah hi hai jisne tumhein paida kiya, tumko sunney aur dekhne ki taaqatein di aur sochne samajhne waley dil diye, magar tum kam hi shukr ada karte ho"
  67,24,"Insey kaho, Allah hi hai jisne tumhein zameen mein phailaya hai aur usi ki taraf tum sametey jaogey"
  67,25,Yeh kehte hain “Agar tum sacchey ho to batao yeh wada kab poora hoga?”
  67,26,"Kaho “Iska ilm to Allah ke paas hai, main to bas saaf saaf khabardar kardene wala hoon"
  67,27,"Phir jab yeh us cheez ko kareeb dekh lenge to un sab logon ke chehre bigad jayenge jinhon ne inkar kiya hai, aur us waqt unse kaha jayega ke yahi hai woh cheez jiske liye tum takazey kar rahey (ask for) thay"
  67,28,"Insey kaho, kabhi tumne yeh bhi socha ke Allah khwa mujhey aur mere saathiyon ko halaaq karde ya hum par Reham karey, kafiron ko dardnaak azaab se kaun bacha lega"
  67,29,"Insey kaho, woh bada Raheem hai, usi par hum imaan laye hain, aur usi par hamara bharosa hai, ankareeb tumhein maloom ho jayega ke sareeh gumrahi (manifest error) mein pada hua kaun hai"
  67,30,"Inse kaho, kabhi tumne yeh bhi socha ke agar tumhare kuwon (wells) ka pani zameen mein utar jaye to kaun hai jo is pani ki behti hui sotein (flowing water) tumhein nikal kar la dega"
  68,1,"Noon, Kasam hai qalam ki aur us cheez ki jisey likhne waley likh rahey hain"
  68,2,Tum apne Rubb ke fazl se majnoon (deewane) nahin ho
  68,3,Aur yaqeenan tumhare liye aisa ajar (reward) hai jiska silsila kabhi khatm honay wala nahin
  68,4,Aur beshak tum akhlaaq ke bade martabe par ho
  68,5,Anqareeb tum bhi dekh logey aur woh bhi dekh lenge
  68,6,Ke tum mein se kaun junoon (madness) mein mubtala hai
  68,7,"Tumhara Rubb un logon ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo uski raah se bhatkey huey hain , aur wahi unko bhi acchi tarah jaanta hai jo raah-e-raast par hai"
  68,8,Lihaza tum in jhutlane walon ke dabao mein hargiz na aao
  68,9,yeh to chahte hain ke kuch tum mudahnat (narmi) karo to yeh bhi mudahnat (narmi) karein
  68,10,Hargiz na dabo kisi aisey shaks se jo bahut kasmein khane wala be-waqaat (worthless) aadmi hai
  68,11,"Taaney deta hai , chugliyan khata phirta hai (slanderer, gossip-monger)"
  68,12,"Bhalayi se rokta hai , zulm-o-zyadti mein hadd se guzar janey wala hai, sakht badh-amal hai , jafa-kaar hai"
  68,13,Aur in sab uyub (aib) ke saath badh-asl (illegitimate child) hai
  68,14,Is bina par ke woh bahut maal-o-aulad rakhta hai
  68,15,Jab hamari aayat usko sunayi jati hai to kehta hai yeh to agle waqton ke afsane hain
  68,16,Ankareeb hum iski sund (snout) par daag lagayenge
  68,17,"Humne in (ehle makkah) ko usi taraah aazmaish mein dala hai jis tarah ek baagh (garden) ke maalikon ko aazmaish mein dala tha, jab unhon ne kasam khayi ke subah sawerey zaroor apne baagh ke phal todenge"
  68,18,Aur woh koi istasna (exception) nahin kar rahey thay
  68,19,Raat ko woh soye padey thay ke tumhare Rubb ki taraf se ek balaa is baagh par phir gayi
  68,20,Aur uska haal aisa ho gaya jaise kati hui fasal ho
  68,21,Subah un logon ne ek dusre ko pukara
  68,22,Kaha agar phal todne hai ho to sawerey sawerey apni kheti ki taraf nikal chalo
  68,23,Chunanchey woh chal padey aur aapas mein chupke chupke kehte jatay thay
  68,24,Ke aaj koi miskeen tumhare paas baag mein na aane paye
  68,25,Woh kuch na dene ka faisla kiye huye subah sawerey jaldi jaldi is tarah wahan gaye jaise ke woh (phal todne par) qadir hain
  68,26,Magar jab baagh ko dekha to kehne lagey “hum raasta bhool gaye hain
  68,27,Nahin balke hum mehroom reh gaye”
  68,28,Un mein jo sab se behtar aadmi tha usne kaha “maine tumse kaha na tha ke tum tasbeeh kyun nahin karte?”
  68,29,"Woh pukar utthey paak hai hamara Rubb, waqayi hum gunahgaar thay"
  68,30,Phir unmein se har ek dusre ko malamat karne laga
  68,31,"Akhir ko unhon ne kaha “afsos hamare haal par, beshak hum sarkash ho gaye thay"
  68,32,"Baeed (door) nahin ke hamara Rubb humein badle mein issey behtar baagh ata farmaye, hum apne Rubb ki taraf rujoo karte hain"
  68,33,"Aisa hota hai azaab aur aakhirat ka azaab issey bhi bada hai, kaash yeh log isko jaante"
  68,34,Yaqeenan khuda-tars logon ke liye unke Rubb ke yahan niyamat bhari jannatein hain
  68,35,Kya hum farma-bardaaron ka haal mujreemon sa kardein
  68,36,"Tum logon ko kya ho gaya hai, tum kaise hukum lagate ho"
  68,37,Kya tumhare paas koi kitaab hai jismein tum yeh padhte ho
  68,38,Ke tumhare liye zaroor wahan wahi kuch hai jo tum apne liye pasand karte ho
  68,39,Ya phir kya tumhare liye roz-e-qayamat tak humpar kuch ahad-o-paiman (covenant) sabit hai ke tumhein wahi kuch milega jiska tum hukum lagao
  68,40,Inse pucho tum mein se kaun iska zaamin (gurantee/responsible) hai
  68,41,Ya phir inke thehraye huye kuch sahreek hain (jinhon ne iska zimma liya ho)?yeh baat hai to layein apne shareekon ko agar yeh sacchey hain
  68,42,Jis roz sakht waqt aa padega aur logon ko sajda karne ke liye bulaya jayega to yeh log sajda na kar sakenge
  68,43,"Inki nigaahein nichey hongi, zillat inpar chaa rahi hogi. Yeh jab sahi-o-saalim thay us waqt inhein sajde ke liye (bulaya jata tha) aur yeh inkar karte thay"
  68,44,"Pas aey Nabi, tum is kalam ke jhutlane walon ka maamla mujhpar chodh do hum aise tarike se inko batadreej tabahi ki taraf le jayenge ke inko khabar bhi na hogi"
  68,45,"Main inki rassi daraaz kar raha hoon, meri chaal badi zabardast hai"
  68,46,Kya tum insey koi ajar (compensation) talab kar rahey ho ke yeh is chatti ke bojh (feel burdened with debt) taley dabey ja rahe hoon
  68,47,Kya inke paas gaib ka ilam hai jisey yeh likh rahey hon
  68,48,"Pas apne Rubb ka faisla saadir honay tak sabr karo aur machli wale (younis) ki tarah na ho jao, jab usne pukara tha aur woh gham se bhara hua tha"
  68,49,Agar uske Rubb ki meharbani uske shamil-e-haal na ho jati to woh mazmoom (disgrace) hokar chatyal maidan mein phenk diya jata
  68,50,Aakhir-e-kaar uske Rubb ne usey barguzida (exalted) farma liya aur usey saleh bandon mein shamil kardiya
  68,51,"Jab yeh kafir log kalam-e-nasihat (Quran) sunte hain to tumhein aisi nazaron se dekhte hain ke goya tumhare qadam ukhaad denge, Aur kehte hain ke yeh zaroor deewana hai"
  68,52,Halaanke yeh to sarey jahaan walon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  69,1,"Honi shudhni ! (indubitable) [sach-much honay wali]"
  69,2,Kya hai woh honi shudni (indubitable)
  69,3,Aur tum kya jaano ke woh kya hai honi shudhni (indubitable)
  69,4,Samood aur Aad ne us achanak toot padne wali aafat ko jhutlaya
  69,5,To Samood ek sakht haadse mein halaaq kiye gaye
  69,6,Aur Aad ek badi shadeed toofani aandhi(storm) se tabah kardiye gaye
  69,7,Allah taala ne usko musalsal saat (seven) raat aur aath (eight) din unpar musallat rakkha (tum wahan hotey to) dekhte ke woh wahan is tarah pachade paday jaise woh khajoor ke boseeda (rotten) taney (trunks) hon
  69,8,Ab kya unmein se koi tumhein baki nazar aata hai
  69,9,Aur isi khata-e-azeem ka irtiqaab Firoun aur ussey pehle ke logon ne aur talpat (overturned) ho janey wali bastiyon ne kiya
  69,10,Un sab ne apne Rubb ke Rasool ki baat na maani to usne unko bade sakhti ke saath pakda
  69,11,Jab pani ka toofan hadd se guzar gaya to humne tumko kashti mein sawar kardiya tha
  69,12,Taa-ke is waqiye ko tumhare liye ek sabaq-aamoz yaadgaar bana dein aur yaad rakhne waley kaan iski yaad mehfooz rakkhein
  69,13,Phir jab ek dafa sur mein phoonk maar di jayegi
  69,14,Aur zameen aur pahadon ko utha kar ek hi chot mein reza reza kardiya jayega
  69,15,Us roz woh honay wala waqiya pesh aa jayega
  69,16,Usdin Aasmaan phatega aur uski bandish dhili padh jayegi
  69,17,Farishtey uske atraf-o-jawanib mein hongey aur aat (eight) farishtey us roz tere Rubb ka arsh apne upar uthaye huey hongey
  69,18,"Woh din hoga jab tumlog pesh kiye jaogey, tumhara koi raaz bhi chupa na reh jayega"
  69,19,"Us waqt jiska naam-e-aamal uske seedhey haath mein diya jayega woh kahega “lo dekho, padho mera naam-e-aamal"
  69,20,Main samajhta tha ke mujhey zaroor apna hisaab milne wala hai”
  69,21,Pas woh dil pasand aish mein hoga
  69,22,Aali muqaam jannat mein
  69,23,Jiske phalon ke guchhey jhuke padh rahey hongey
  69,24,(Aise logon se kaha jayega) mazey se khao aur pio apne un aamal ke badle jo tumne guzre huey dino mein kiye hain
  69,25,Aur jiska naam-e-aamal uske bayein (left) haath mein diya jayega woh kahega “ kaash mera aamal nama mujhey na diya gaya hota
  69,26,Aur main na jaanta ke mera hisaab kya hai
  69,27,Kaash meri wahi maut (jo duniya mei aayi thi) faisla-kun hoti
  69,28,Aaj mera maal mere kuch kaam na aaya
  69,29,Mera sara iqtedaar khatam ho gaya
  69,30,(hukum hoga) pakdo isey aur iski gardan mei touk daal do
  69,31,Phir isey jahannum mein jhoonk do
  69,32,Phir isko satter(seventy) haath lambi zanjeer mei jakad do
  69,33,Yeh na Allah buzurg-o-bartar par iman lata tha
  69,34,Aur na miskeen ko khana khilane ki targeeb deta tha
  69,35,Lihaza aaj na yahan iska koi yaar-e-gamkhaar hai
  69,36,Aur na zakhmon ke dhowan (washing of wounds) ke siwa iske liye koi khana
  69,37,Jisey khatakaaron (sinners) ke siwa koi nahin khata
  69,38,"Pas nahin, main qasam khata hoon un cheezon ki bhi jo tum dekhte ho"
  69,39,Aur unki bhi jinhein tum nahin dekhte
  69,40,Yeh ek Rasool-e-kareem ka qaul ( speech ) hai
  69,41,"Kisi shayar ka qaul nahin hai, tumlog kam hi iman latey ho"
  69,42,"Aur na yeh kisi kaahin(soothsayer) ka qaul hai , tum log kam hi gaur karte ho"
  69,43,Yeh Rabb-ul alameen ki taraf se nazil huwa hai
  69,44,Aur agar is (Nabi) ne khud ghad kar koi baat hamari taraf mansook ki hoti
  69,45,To hum iska dayan(right) haath padkad letay
  69,46,Aur iski rag-e-gardan (life vein) kaat daalte
  69,47,Phir tum mein se koi (humein)is kaam se rokne wala na hota
  69,48,Dar haqeeqat yeh parheizgar logon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  69,49,Aur hum jante hain ke tum mein se kuch log jhutlane waley hain
  69,50,Aise kafiron ke liye yaqeenan yeh mujeeb-e-hasrat (cause of regret) hai
  69,51,Aur yeh bilkul yaqeeni haqq hai
  69,52,"Pas aey nabi, apne Rubb-e-azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
  70,1,Mangne waley ne azaab maanga hai (woh azaab) jo zaroor waqey honay wala hai
  70,2,"Kafiron ke liye hai, koi usey dafa karne wala nahin"
  70,3,Us khuda ki taraf se hai jo urooj ke zeeno (ascending steps)ka malik hai
  70,4,Malaika (angels) aur rooh(Jibrael) uske huzoor chadh kar jatey hain ek aise din mein jiski miqdar pacchas (fifty) hazar saal hai
  70,5,"Pas aey Nabi, sabr karo, shaista sabr"
  70,6,Yeh log usey dur samajhte hain
  70,7,Aur hum usey qareeb dekh rahey hain
  70,8,(woh azaab us roz hoga) jis roz aasman pigli huye chandi ki tarah ho jayega
  70,9,Aur pahad rang-bi-rang ke dhunke huey oon (wool) jaise ho jayenge
  70,10,Aur koi jigri dost apne jigri dost ko na puchega
  70,11,"Halaanke woh ek dusre ko dikhaye jayenge, mujrim chahega ke us din ke azaab se bachne ke liye apni aulad ko"
  70,12,"Apni biwi ko, apne bhai ko"
  70,13,Apne qareeb-tareen khandaan ko jo usey panaah dene wala tha
  70,14,Aur rooh-e-zameen ke sab logon ko fidiya (badle) mein dey-de aur yeh tadbeer usey nijaat dila de
  70,15,Hargiz nahin woh to bhadakti hui aag ki lapat hogi
  70,16,Jo gosht posht ko chaat jayegi
  70,17,Pukar pukar kar apni taraf bulayegi har us shaks ko jisne haqq se mooh moda aur peet pheri
  70,18,Aur maal jamaa kiya aur seint seint kar (amassed wealth) rakkha
  70,19,Insan thud-dila (impatient) paida kiya gaya hai
  70,20,Jab uspar museebat aati hai to ghabra uthta hai
  70,21,Aur jab usey khush-haali naseeb hoti hai to bukhl (kanjoosi) karne lagta hai
  70,22,Magar woh log (is aib se bache huey hai) jo namaz padne waley hain
  70,23,Jo apni namaz ki hamesha pabandi karte hai
  70,24,Jinke maalon mein
  70,25,Saahil (maangne waley) aur mehroom ka ek haqq mukarrar hai
  70,26,Jo roz-e-jaza ko barhaq maante hain
  70,27,Jo apne Rubb ke azaab se darte hain
  70,28,Kyunke unke Rubb ka azaab aisi cheez nahin hai jissey koi bekhauf ho
  70,29,Jo apni sharmgahon ki hifazat karte hain
  70,30,Ba-juz apne biwiyon ya apni mamluka aurton ke jinse mehfooz na rakhne mein unpar koi malamat nahin
  70,31,Albatta jo iske alawa kuch aur chahein wahi hadd se tajawuz karne wala hai
  70,32,Jo apne amanaton ki hifazat aur apne ahad (covenant) ka paas karte hai
  70,33,Jo apni gawahiyon mein raast baazi (upright) par qayam rehte hain
  70,34,Aur jo apni namaz ki hifazat karte hain
  70,35,Yeh log izzat ke saath jannat ke baaghon mei rahenge
  70,36,"Pas aey Nabi , kya baat hai ke yeh munkirin dayein(left) aur bayein(right) se"
  70,37,Giroh (crowds) dar giroh(crowds) tumhari taraf daude chale aa rahe hain
  70,38,Kya inmein se har ek yeh lalaj rakhta hai ke woh niyamat bhari jannat mein daakhil kardiya jayega
  70,39,Hargiz nahin humne jis cheez se inko paida kiya hai usey yeh khud jaante hain
  70,40,"Pas nahin, main qasam khata hoon mashrikon aur maghribon ke maalik ki hum ispar qadir hain"
  70,41,Ke inki jagah insey behtar log le aayein aur koi humse baazi le jaane wala nahin hai
  70,42,Lihaza inhein apni behuda baaton aur apne khel mein pada rehne do yahan tak ke yeh apne us din ko pahunch jayenge jiska insey waada kiya ja raha hai
  70,43,Jab yeh apni qabron se nikal kar is tarah daude ja rahey hongey jaise apne buthon (idols) ke aasthano (altars) ki taraf daud rahey hon
  70,44,"Inki nigahein jhuki hui hongi, zillat inpar chaa rahi hogi, woh din hai jiska insey wada kiya ja raha hai"
  71,1,Humne Nooh ko uski qaum ki taraf bheja (is hidayat ke saath) ke apni qaum ke logon ko khabardar karde qabl iske ke unpar ek dardnaak azaab aaye
  71,2,"Usne kaha “ Aey meri qaum ke logon, main tumhare liye ek saaf saaf khabardar kardene wala (paighambar) hoon"
  71,3,(Tumko aagah karta hoon) ke Allah ki bandagi karo aur ussey daro aur meri itaat (follow) karo
  71,4,Allah tumhare gunaahon se darguzar farmayega aur tumhein ek waqt-e-mukarrar tak baaki rakkhega. Haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ka mukarrar kiya hua waqt jab aa jata hai to phir taala nahin jata kaash tumhein iska ilm ho
  71,5,"Usne arz kiya “Aey mere Rubb , maine apni qaum ke logon ko shab-o-roz (night and day) pukara"
  71,6,Magar meri pukar ne unke farar hi mei izafa kiya
  71,7,"Aur jab bhi maine unko bulaya taa-ke tu unhein maaf karde , unhon ne kaano mein ungliyan thoos li aur apne kapdon se mooh dhaank liye aur apni rawish par adh gaye aur bada takabbur (proudness) kiya"
  71,8,Phir maine unko haanke pukarey (openly) ki dawat di
  71,9,Phir maine aelaniya (publicly) bhi unko tableeg ki aur chupke chupke bhi samjhaya
  71,10,"Maine kaha apne Rubb se maafi maango,beshak woh bada maaf karne wala hai"
  71,11,Woh tumpar aasmaan se khoob baarishein barsayega
  71,12,"Tumhein maal aur aulad se nawaze ga, tumhare liye baagh paida karega aur tumhare liye nehrein jaari kardega"
  71,13,Tumhein kya ho gaya hai ke Allah ke liye tum kisi waqar (majesty) ki tawakku nahin rakhte
  71,14,Halaanke usne tarah tarah se tumhein banaya hai
  71,15,Kya dekhte nahin ho ke Allah ne kis tarah saat aasman teh-bar-teh banaye
  71,16,Aur unmein chand ko noor aur suraj ko chiraag banaya
  71,17,Aur Allah ne tumko zameen se ajeeb tarah ugaya
  71,18,Phir woh tumhein isi zameen mein wapas le jayega aur issey yakayak tumko nikal khada karega
  71,19,Aur Allah ne zameen ko tumhare liye farsh ki tarah bicha diya
  71,20,Taa-ke tum uske andar khule raaston mein chalo
  71,21,"Nooh ne kaha “mere Rubb, unhon ne meri baat radd kardi aur un (raheeson) ki pairvi ki jo maal aur aulad paa kar aur zyada na murad ho gaye hain"
  71,22,In logon ne bada bhaari makr (plot) ka jaal phaila rakkha hai
  71,23,"Inhon ne kaha hargiz na chodo apne maboodon (deities) ko, aur na chodo Wadd aur Suwa ko aur na Yagus aur Yaook aur Nasr ko (idol names)"
  71,24,"Inhon ne bahut logon ko gumraah kiya hai, aur tu bhi in zalimon ko gumrahi ke siwa kisi cheez mein tarakki na de"
  71,25,"Apni khataon ki bina par hi woh garq(drown) kiye gaye aur Aag mein jhoonk diye gaye , phir unhon ne apne liye Allah se bachane wala koi madadgar na paya"
  71,26,"Aur Nooh ne kaha “Mere Rubb, In kafiron mein se koi zameen par basne wala na chodh"
  71,27,Agar tu ne inko chodh diya to yeh tere bandon ko gumraah karenge aur inki nasal se jo bhi paida hoga badkar aur sakht kafir hi hoga
  71,28,"Mere Rubb, mujhey aur mere waldain ko aur har us shaks ko jo mere ghar mein momin ki haisiyat se dakhil hua hai, Aur sab momin mardon aur auraton ko maaf farma de, Aur zalimon ke liye halakat ke siwa kisi cheez mein izafa na kar"
  72,1,"Aey Nabi, kaho, meri taraf wahee (revelation) bheji gayi hai ke Jinno ke ek giroh (group) ne gaur se suna phir (jaa kar apne qaum ke logon se) kaha: “humne ek bada hi ajeeb Quran suna hai"
  72,2,Jo raah-e-raast ki taraf rehnumayi karta hai is liye hum uspar iman le aaye hain aur ab hum hargiz apne Rubb ke saath kisi ko sharik nahin karenge
  72,3,"Aur yeh ke hamare Rubb ki shaan bahut aala-o-Arfa hai , usne kisi ko biwi ya beta nahin banaya"
  72,4,Aur yeh ke hamare nadaan log Allah ke barey mein bahut khilaf-e-haqq baatein karte rahey hain
  72,5,Aur yeh ke humne samjha tha ke insaan aur jinn kabhi khuda ke baarey mein jhoot nahin bol sakte
  72,6,"Aur yeh ke Insano mein se kuch log Jinno mein se kuch logon ki panaah (refuge) maanga karte thay, is tarah unhon ne Jinno ka guroor aur zyada badha diya"
  72,7,Aur yeh ke insaano ne bhi wahi gumaan kiya jaisa tumhara gumaan tha ke Allah kisi ko Rasool bana kar na bhejega
  72,8,Aur yeh ke humne aasman ko tatola to dekha ke woh pehray-daaron (terrible guards) se patha pada hai aur shahabon (shooting meteors) ki baarish ho rahi hai
  72,9,"Aur yeh ke pehle hum sun-gun lene ke liye aasman mei baithnay ki jagah paa lete thay, magar ab jo chori chupey sunne ke koshish karta hai woh apne liye ghaat mein ek shahabe saaqib (shooting meteors) laga hua paata hai"
  72,10,Aur yeh ke hamari samajh mein na aata tha ke aaya zameen walon ke saath koi bura maamla karne ka irada kiya gaya hai ya unka Rubb unhein raah-e-raast dikhana chahta hai
  72,11,"Aur yeh ke hum mein se kuch log saleh (upright) hain aur kuch is se farotar hain, hum mukhtalif tareeqon (ways/factions) mein batey (divided) huey hain"
  72,12,Auy yeh ke hum samajhte thay ke na zameen mein hum Allah ko aajiz (frustrate) kar sakte hain aur na bhaag kar usey hara saktey hain
  72,13,Aur yeh ke humne jab hidayat ki taleem suni to hum uspar iman le aaye ab jo koi bhi apne Rubb par iman le aayega usey kisi haq-talfi ya zulm ka khauff na hoga
  72,14,Aur yeh ke hum mein se kuch muslim(Allah ke itaat guzar) hain aur kuch haqq se munharif (upright) to jinhon ne Islam (itaat ka raasta) ikhtiyar kar liya unhon ne najaat ki raah dhoond li
  72,15,Aur jo haqq se muhnarif hai woh jahannum ka indhan (fuel) banney wala hai
  72,16,Aur (aey Nabi kaho mujhpar yeh wahee bhi ki gayi hai ke) log agar raah-e-raast par sabit qadami (firmly) se chalte to hum unhein khoob sairaab karte (provide abundant rain)
  72,17,Taa-ke is niyamat se unki aazmaish karein aur jo apne Rubb ke zikr se mooh modega uska Rubb usey sakht azaab mein mubtala kardega
  72,18,"Aur yeh ke masjidein Allah ke liye hai, lihaza unmein Allah ke saath kisi aur ko na pukaro"
  72,19,Aur yeh ke jab Allah ka banda usko pukarne ke liye khada hua to log uspar toot padne ke liye tayyar ho gaye
  72,20,"Aey Nabi ,kaho ke main to apne Rubb ko pukarta hoon aur uske saath kisi ko sharik nahin karta"
  72,21,Kaho main tum logon keliye na kisi nuksan ka ikhtiyar rakhta hoon na kisi bhalayi ka
  72,22,Kaho mujhey Allah ki giraft se koi nahin bacha sakta aur na main uske daaman ke siwa koi jaye panaah (refuge) paa sakta hoon
  72,23,Mera kaam iske siwa kuch nahin hai ke Allah ki baat aur uske paighamaat pahuncha doon. Ab jo bhi Allah aur uske Rasool ki baat na maanega uske liye jahannum ki aag hai aur aisey log usmein hamesha rahenge
  72,24,(Yeh log apni is rawish se baaz na aayenge) yahan tak ke jab us cheez ko dekh lenge jiska inse waada kiya ja raha hai to inhein maloom ho jayega ke kiske madadgaar kamzoar hain aur kiska jattha (group) taadad mein kam hai
  72,25,"Kaho, main nahin jaanta ke jis cheez ka waada tumse kiya ja raha hai woh qareeb hai ya mera Rubb uske liye koi lambi muddat muqarrar famata hai"
  72,26,"Woh aalimul gaib hai , apne gaib par kisi ko muttala (reveal/disclose) nahin karta"
  72,27,"Siwai us Rasool ke jisey usne (gaib ka koi ilm dene ke liye) pasand karliya ho, to uske aagey aur pichey woh muhafiz (guards) laga deta hai"
  72,28,"Taa-ke woh jaan le ke unhon ne apne Rubb ke paighamaat pahuncha diye, aur woh unke poorey maahol ka ihata (encompass) kiye huey hai aur ek ek cheez ko usne gin rakkha hai"
  73,1,Aey oad lapet kar (enwrapped ) sone waley
  73,2,Raat ko namaz mein khade raha karo magar kam
  73,3,Aadhi Raat
  73,4,"Ya issey kuch kam karlo ya issey kuch zyada badha do, aur Quran ko khoob tehar tehar kar padho"
  73,5,Hum tumpar ek bhari kalam nazil karne waley hain
  73,6,Dar haqeeqat raat ka uthna nafs par qaabu paney ke liye bahut kaargar aur Quran theek padhne ke liye zyada mauzu (suitable) hai
  73,7,Din ke auqat mein to tumhare liye bahut masrufiyat (prolonged occupation) hai
  73,8,Apne Rubb ke naam ka zikr kiya karo aur sabse katt kar usi ke ho raho
  73,9,"Woo mashrik (east) o magrib (west) ka maalik hai, uske siwa koi khuda nahin hai, lihaza usi ko apna wakeel bana lo"
  73,10,Aur jo baatein log bana rahey hain unpar sabr karo aur sharafat ke saath unse alag ho jao
  73,11,In jhutlane waley khush haal logon se nimatne ka kaam tum mujhpar chodh do aur inhein zara kuch dair isi halat par rehne do
  73,12,Hamarey paas (inke liye) bhaari bediyan hain aur bhadakti hui aag
  73,13,Aur halaq(throat) mein phasne wala khana aur dard-naak azaab
  73,14,Yeh us din hoga jab zameen aur pahad laraz uthengey aur pahadon ka haal aisa ho jaeyga jaise reit (sand) ke dhair hai jo bhikhre ja rahe hain
  73,15,Tum logon ke paas humne usi tarah ek rasool tum par gawah bana kar bheja hai jis tarah humne Firaun ki taraf ek rasool bheja tha
  73,16,(Phir dekhlo ke jab ) Firaun ne us Rasool ki baat na maani to humne usko badi sakhti kay saath pakad liya
  73,17,Agar tum maan-ne se inkar karoge to us din kaisey bach jaogey jo bacchon ko boodha kardega
  73,18,Aur jiski sakhti se aasman phata ja raha hoga?Allah ka wada to poora hokar hi rehna hai
  73,19,"Yeh ek nasihat hai , ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf janey ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  73,20,"Aey Nabi, tumhara Rubb janta hai ke tum kabhi do tihayi (two-third) raat ke qareeb aur kabhi aadhi raat aur kabhi ek tihayi (one-third) raat ibadat mein khade rehtey ho,Aur tumhare saathiyon mein se bhi ek giroh yeh amal karta hai, Allah hi raat aur din ke auqat ka hisab rakhta hai. Usey maloom hai ke tumlog auqat ka theek shumar nahin kar sakte, lihaza usne tumpar meharbani farmayi, Ab jitna Quran aasani se padh sakte ho padh liya karo. Usey maloom hai ke tum mein kuch mareez hongey, kuch dusre log Allah ke fazal(bounty) ki talash mein safar karte hain, Aur kuch aur log Allah ki raah mein jung karte hain, pas jitna Quran ba aasani padha ja sakey padh liya karo, namaz qayam karo, zakaat do aur Allah ko accha qarz dete raho, jo kuch bhalayi tum apne liye aagey bhejoge usey Allah ke yahan maujood paogey, wahi zyada behtar hai aur uska ajr bahut bada hai. Allah se magfirat maangte raho, beshak Allah bada Gafoor o Raheem hai"
  74,1,Aey oad lapeit (enveloped) kar laitney waley
  74,2,Utho aur khabardar karo
  74,3,Aur apne Rubb ki badayi ka elan karo
  74,4,Aur apne kapde paak rakho
  74,5,Aur gandagi se dur raho
  74,6,Aur ehsan na karo zyada hasil karne keliye
  74,7,Aur apne Rubb ki khatir sabr karo
  74,8,Accha jab soor mein phook maari jayegi
  74,9,Woh din bada hi sakht din hoga
  74,10,Kafiron ke liye halka na hoga
  74,11,Chodh do mujhey aur us shaks ko jisey maine akela paida kiya hai
  74,12,Bahut sa maal usko diya
  74,13,Uske saath hazir rehne waley bete diye
  74,14,Aur uske liye riyasat ki raah hamwaar ki
  74,15,Phir woh tama (greedily desire) rakhta hai ke main usey aur zyada doon
  74,16,Hargiz nahin woh hamari ayaat se inaath(stubbornly oppose) rakhta hai
  74,17,Main to usey ankareeb ek kathin chadhai chadwaunga
  74,18,Usne socha aur kuch baat banane ki koshish ki
  74,19,"To khuda ki maar uspar, kaisi baat banane ki koshish ki"
  74,20,"Haan, khuda ki maar uspar , kaisi baat banane ki koshish ki"
  74,21,Phir(logon ki taraf) dekha
  74,22,Phir peshani sukedi aur mooh banaya
  74,23,Phir palta aur takabbur mein padh gaya
  74,24,Aakhir e kaar bola ke yeh kuch nahin hai magar ek jaadu jo pehle se chala aa raha hai
  74,25,Yeh to ek Insani kalaam hai
  74,26,Anqareeb main usey dozakh mei jhonk dunga
  74,27,Aur tum kya jaano ke kya hai woh dozakh
  74,28,Na baqi rakhey na chodey
  74,29,Khaal(skin) jhulas dene wali
  74,30,Unnis (ninteen) karkoon uspar muqarrar hain
  74,31,"Humne dozakh ke yeh karkoon farishtey banaye hain,aur unki tadaad ko kafiron ke liye fitna bana diya hai, taa-ke ehle kitaab ko yaqeen aa jaye aur iman laney walon ka iman badhey,Aur ehle kitaab aur momineen kisi shakk mein na rahey,aur dil ke bimar aur kuffar yeh kahein ke bhala Allah ka is ajeeb baat se kya matlab ho sakta hai. Is tarah Allah jisey chahta hai gumraah kardeta hai aur jisey chahta hai hidayat baksh deta hai aur tere Rubb ke lashkaron (soldiers) ko khud uske siwa koi nahin janta, aur is dozak ka zikr iske siwa kisi garz ke liye nahin kiya gaya hai ke logon ko issey naseehat ho"
  74,32,"Hargiz nahin,kasam hai Chand ki"
  74,33,Aur Raat ki jabke woh palat-ti hai
  74,34,Aur subah ki jabke woh roshan hoti hai
  74,35,Yeh dozakh bhi badi cheezon mein se ek hai
  74,36,Insano ke liye darawa
  74,37,Tum mein se har us shaks ke liye darawa jo aagey badhna chahey ya pichey reh jana chahey
  74,38,"Har mutanaffis, apne kasb ke badle rehan hai (hostage to one’s deeds)"
  74,39,Dayein bazu walon ke siwa
  74,40,"Jo jannaton mein hongey, wahan woh"
  74,41,Mujrimon se puchenge
  74,42,Tumhein kya cheez dozakh mein le gayi
  74,43,woh kahenge “hum namaz padne walon mein se na thay
  74,44,Aur miskeen ko khana nahin khilate thay
  74,45,Aur haqq ke khilaf batein banane walon ke saath milkar hum bhi batein banane lagte thay
  74,46,Aur roz-e-jaza ko jhoot karar dete thay
  74,47,Yahan tak ke humein us yaqeeni cheez se saabqa pesh aa gaya”
  74,48,Us waqt sifarish karne walon ki sifarish unke kisi kaam na ayegi
  74,49,Aakhir in logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh is nasihat se mooh moad rahey hain
  74,50,Goya yeh jungli gadhey hain
  74,51,Jo Sher se darr kar bhaag padey hain
  74,52,Balke inmein se to har ek yeh chahta hai ke uske naam khule khat (scroll/scripture) bhejey jaye
  74,53,"Hargiz nahin, Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh aakhirat ka khauf nahin rakhtey"
  74,54,"Hargiz nahin,yeh to ek nasihat hai"
  74,55,Ab jiska jee chahey issey sabaq hasil karle
  74,56,Aur yeh koi sabaq hasil na karengey illa yeh ke Allah hi aisa chahey woh iska haqdar hai ke ussey taqwa kiya jaye aur woh iska ehal hai ke (taqwa karne walon ko) baksh de
  75,1,Nahin main kasam khata hoon qayamat ke din ki
  75,2,"Aur nahin,main kasam khata hoon malamat karne wale nafs ki"
  75,3,Kya Insan yeh samajh raha hai ke hum uski haddiyon ko jama na kar sakengey
  75,4,Kyun nahin? Hum to uski ungliyon ke por por tak theek bana dene par qadir hain
  75,5,Magar Insan chahta yeh hai ke aagey bhi badh-aamaliyan karta rahey
  75,6,“Puchta hai” aakhir kab aana hai woh qayamat ka din
  75,7,Phir jab dedhey pathra jayengey (sight is dazed)
  75,8,Aur chand be-noor ho jayega
  75,9,Aur Chand Suraj mila kar ek kardiya jayenge
  75,10,Us waqt yahi Insan kahega kahan bhaag kar jaun
  75,11,"Hargiz nahin,wahan koi jaye panaah na hogi"
  75,12,Us roz terey Rubb hi ke samney jaakar theharna hoga
  75,13,Us roz Insan ko uska sab agla pichla kiya karaya bata diya jayega
  75,14,Balke Insan khud hi apne aap ko khoob janta hai
  75,15,Chahey woh kitni hi maazratein (excuses) karey
  75,16,"Aey Nabi , Is wahi ko jaldi jaldi yaad karne ke liye apni zubaan ko harkat na do"
  75,17,Isko yaad kara dena aur padhwa dena hamare zimmey hai
  75,18,Lihaza jab hum isey padh rahey hon us waqt tum iske qirat ko gaur se sunte raho
  75,19,Phir iska matlab samjha dena bhi hamarey zimmey hai
  75,20,"Hargiz nahin, asal baat yeh hai ke tum log jaldi haasil honay wali cheez (yani duniya) se muhabbat rakhte ho"
  75,21,Aur aakhirat ko chodh dete ho
  75,22,Us roz kuch chehrey tar-o-taza hongey
  75,23,Apne Rubb ki taraf dekh rahey hongey
  75,24,Aur kuch chehrey udas hongey
  75,25,Aur samajh rahey hongey ke unke saath qamar-todh bartao hone wala hai
  75,26,"Hargiz nahin, jab jaan halaq tak pahunch jayegi"
  75,27,Aur kaha jayega ke hai koi jhaad phook karne wala
  75,28,Aur aadmi samajh lega ke yeh duniya se judai ka waqt hai
  75,29,Aur pindli(leg) se pindli(leg) judh jayegi
  75,30,Woh din hoga tere Rubb ki taraf rawangi ka
  75,31,"Magar usne na sach mana , aur na namaz padhi"
  75,32,Balke jhutlaya aur palat gaya
  75,33,Phir akadta hua apne ghar walon ki taraf chal diya
  75,34,Yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,35,Haan yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,36,"Kya Insan ne yeh samajh rakkha hai ke woh yunhi mohmal (left alone, unquestioned )chodh diya jayega"
  75,37,Kya woh ek hakeer pani ka nutfa (sperm from semen) na tha jo (raham –e-madar mei) tapkaya jata hai
  75,38,"Phir woh ek lothda(clot) bana, phir Allah ne uska jism banaya aur uske aazaa durust kiye"
  75,39,Phir ussey mard aur aurat ki do qismein banayi
  75,40,Kya woh ispar qadir nahin hai ke marne walon ko phir zinda karde
  76,1,Kya Insan par la mutanahi zamane ka ek waqt aisa bhi guzra hai jab woh koi qabil e zikr cheez na tha
  76,2,Humne Insan ko ek makhlut nutfey (intermingled sperm) se paida kiya taa-ke uska imtihaan lein aur is garz ke liye humne usey sunne aur dekhne wala banaya
  76,3,"Humne usey rasta dikha diya, khwa shukar karne wala baney ya kufr karne wala"
  76,4,Kufr karne walon ke liye humne zanjeerein aur tauq (fetters) aur bhadakti hui aag muhaiyya kar rakkhi hai
  76,5,Neik log (jannat mein) sharaab ke aisey sagar piyenge jinmein aabey kafoor ki aamezish (mixture) hogi
  76,6,Yeh ek behta chasma(spring) hoga jiske pani ke saath Allah ke bandey sharaab piyengey aur jahan chahengey ba-sahulat uski shakhein (nikal) lengey
  76,7,"Yeh woh log hongey jo (duniya mein) nazar poori karte hain, aur us din se darte hain jiski aafat har taraf phaili hui hogi"
  76,8,Aur Allah ki muhabbat mein miskeen aur yateem aur qaidi ko khana khilate hain
  76,9,"Aur unse kehte hain ke (hum tumhein sirf) Allah ki khatir khila rahey hain, hum tumse na koi badla chahte hain na shukriya"
  76,10,Humey to apne Rubb se us din ke azaab ka khauf lahiq hai jo sakht museebat ka intehayi taweel din hoga
  76,11,Pas Allah taala unhein us din ke sharr se bacha lega aur unhein taazgi aur suroor bakshega
  76,12,Aur unke sabr ke badle mein unhein jannat aur reshmi libas ata karega
  76,13,"Wahan woh unchey masnadon par takiye lagaye baithey hongey, na unhein dhoop ki garmi satayegi na jaadey ki thirr (bitter cold)"
  76,14,"Jannat ki chaaon unpar jhuki hui saaya kar rahi hogi,aur uske phal har waqt unke bas mein hongey(ke jis tarah chahey unhein todh lein)"
  76,15,Unke aagey chandi ke bartan aur sheshey ke pyale gardish karaye ja rahey hongey
  76,16,"Sheshey bhi woh jo chandi ki qisam ke hongey,aur unko (muntazmin-e-jannat nay)theek andazey ke mutabik bhara hoga"
  76,17,Unko wahan aisi sharaab ke jaam pilaye jayenge jis mein soont (ginger) ki aamezish hogi
  76,18,Yeh jannat ka ek chasma hoga jisey salsabil kaha jata hai
  76,19,Unki khidmat ke liye aisey ladke daudte phir rahey hongey jo hamesha ladke hi rahenge.Tum unhein dekho to samjho ke moti(pearls) hai jo bikhair diye gaye hain
  76,20,Wahan jidhar bhi tum nigah dalogey niyamatein hi niyamatein aur ek badi sultanat ka sar o saman tumhein nazar aayega
  76,21,"Unke upar bareek resham ke sabz libas aur atlas o deba ke kapde (rich brocade)hongey, unko chandi ke kangan pehnaye jayenge , aur unka Rubb unko nihayat pakeeza sharaab pilaeyga"
  76,22,Yeh hai tumhari jaza aur tumhari kaar-guzari qabil-e-qadr thehri hai
  76,23,"Aey Nabi, humne hi tumpar yeh Quran thoda thoda karke nazil kiya hai"
  76,24,"Lihaza tum apne Rubb ke hukum par sabr karo, aur in mein se kisi badh-amal ya munkir-e-haq ki baat na maano"
  76,25,Apne Rubb ka naam subh-o-shaam yaad karo
  76,26,"Raat ko bhi uske huzoor sajda raiz ho, Aur raat ke taveel auqat mein uski tasbeeh karte raho"
  76,27,Yeh log to jaldi hasil honay wali cheez (duniya ) se muhabbat rakhte hai aur aagey jo bhaari din aane wala hai usey nazar andaz kardetey hain
  76,28,"Humne hi inko paida kiya hai aur inke jodh bandh mazboot kiye hai, aur hum jab chahein inki shakalon ko badal kar rakh dein"
  76,29,"Yeh ek nasihat hai,ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf jaane ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  76,30,"Aur tumharey chahne se kuch nahin hota jab tak ke Allah na chachey, yaqeenan Allah bada Aleem-o-Haqeem hai"
  76,31,"Apni rehmat mein jisko chahta hai daakhil karta hai, Aur zalimon ke liye usne dardnaak azaab tayyar kar rakkha hai"
  77,1,Kasam hai un ( hawaon) ki jo pai dar pai bheji jati hain
  77,2,Phir toofani raftar se chalti hai
  77,3,Aur (baadalon ko) utha kar phailati hai
  77,4,Phir (unko) phaad kar juda karti hai
  77,5,Phir (dilon mei khuda ki)yaad daalti hai
  77,6,Uzar (justification) ke taur par ya daravey ke taur par
  77,7,Jis cheez ka tumse wada kiya ja raha hai woh zaroor waqey honay wali hai
  77,8,Phir jab sitarey maand (extinguish) pad jayengey
  77,9,Aur aasmaan phaad diya jayega
  77,10,Aur pahad dhunak daaley jayengey (blown away)
  77,11,Aur Rasoolon ki haziri ka waqt aa pahunchega (us roz woh cheez waqey ho jaeygi)
  77,12,Kis roz ke liye yeh kaam utha rakha gaya hai
  77,13,Faisley ke roz ke liye
  77,14,Aur tumhein kya khabar ke woh faisley ka din kya hai
  77,15,Tabahi hai us din jhutlane walon ke liye
  77,16,Kya humne aglon ko halaq nahin kiya
  77,17,Phir unhi ke pichey hum baad walon ko chalta karengey
  77,18,Mujrimo ke saath hum yahi kuch kiya karte hain
  77,19,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,20,Kya humne ek hakeer pani se tumhein paida nahin kiya
  77,21,Aur ek mukarrara muddat tak
  77,22,Usey ek mehfooz jagah thehraye rakkha
  77,23,"To dekho , hum ispar qadir thay, pas hum bahut acchi qudrat rakhne waley hain"
  77,24,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,25,Kya humne zameen ko sameth kar rakhne wali nahin banaya
  77,26,Zindon ke liye bhi aur murdon ke liye bhi
  77,27,"Aur is mein buland-o-bala pahad jamaye, Aur tumhein meetha pani pilaya"
  77,28,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,29,Chalo ab usi cheez ki taraf jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay
  77,30,Chalo us saaye ki taraf jo teen shaakhon(columns) wala hai
  77,31,Na thandak pahunchane wala aur na aag ki lapat se bachane wala
  77,32,woh aag mahal (castles/fortress) jaisi badi badi chingariyan phenkegi
  77,33,(Jo uchalti hui yun mehsus hongi )goya ke woh zard ount (camel) hai
  77,34,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,35,Yeh woh din hai jismein wo na kuch bolengey
  77,36,Aur na unhein mauka diya jaeyga ke koi uzr(excuse) pesh karein
  77,37,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,38,Yeh faisley ka din hai humne tumhein aur tumse pehle guzrey huey logon ko jamaa kardiya hai
  77,39,Ab agar koi chaal tum chal sakte ho to mere muqabley mein chal dekho
  77,40,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,41,Muttaqi log aaj saayon aur chashmon mein hai
  77,42,Aur jo phal woh chahein (unke liye hazir hai)
  77,43,Khao aur piyo mazey se apne un aamal ke siley mein jo tum karte rahey ho
  77,44,Hum neik logon ko aisi hi jaza detay hain
  77,45,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,46,"Kha lo aur mazey karlo thodey din, haqeeqat mein tum log mujrim ho"
  77,47,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,48,Jab inse kaha jata hai ke (Allah ke aagey) jhuko to nahin jhuktey
  77,49,Tabahi hai uss roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,50,Ab is (Quran) ke baad aur kaunsa kalaam aisa ho sakta hai jispar yeh iman layein
  78,1,Yeh log kis cheez ke baarey mei puch-gajj kar rahe hain
  78,2,Kya us badi khabar ke baarey mein
  78,3,Jiske mutaaliq yeh mukhtalif che-mei-goiyan (disagreement) karne mein lagey huey hain
  78,4,Hargiz nahin an-qareeb inhein maloom ho jayega
  78,5,"Haan hargiz nahin, an-qareeb inhein maloom ho jayega"
  78,6,Kya yeh waqiya nahin hai ke humne zameen ko farsh banaya
  78,7,Aur pahadon ko mekhon(pegs) ki tarah gaad diya
  78,8,Aur tumhein (mardon aur auraton ke) jodon ki shakal mein paida kiya
  78,9,Aur tumhari neend ko baaisey sukoon banaya
  78,10,Aur raat ko purdah posh
  78,11,Aur din ko muaash ka waqt banaya
  78,12,Aur Tumharey upar saat mazboot aasman qayam kiye
  78,13,Aur ek nihayat roshan aur garm chirag paida kya
  78,14,Aur baadalon se lagatar baarish barsayi
  78,15,Taa-ke iske zariye se galla(grain) aur sabzi
  78,16,Aur ghaney baagh ugaye
  78,17,Beshak faisley ka din ek mukarrar waqt hai
  78,18,Jis roz soor mei phook maar di jayegi tum fauj dar fauj nikal aaogey
  78,19,Aur aasmaan khol diya jayega hatta ke woh darwaze hi darwaze ban kar reh jayega
  78,20,Aur pahad chalaye jayenge yahan tak ke woh saraab(mirage) ho jayenge
  78,21,Dar haqeeqat jahannum ek ghaat(ambush) hai
  78,22,Sarkashon ka thikana
  78,23,Jismein woh muddaton padey rahengey
  78,24,Uske andar kisi thandak aur peene ke qabil kisi cheez ka maza woh na chakhengey
  78,25,kuch milega to bas garam paani aur zakhmon ka dho-wan(peep)
  78,26,(Unke kartuton) ka bharpur badla
  78,27,Woh kisi hisab ki tawakku na rakhte thay
  78,28,Aur hamari aayat ko unhon ne bilkul jhutla diya tha
  78,29,Aur haal yeh tha ke humne har cheez gin gin kar likh rakkhi thi
  78,30,"Ab chakho maza, Hum tumhare liye azaab ke siwa kisi cheez mei hargiz izafa na karengey"
  78,31,Yakeenan muttakiyon(pious) ke liye kamrani ka ek Muqaam hai
  78,32,Baagh aur angur
  78,33,Aur naukhez humsin ladkiyan
  78,34,Aur jhalakte huey jaam
  78,35,Wahan koi lagv(vain) aur jhuthi baat woh na sunengey
  78,36,Jazaa aur kafi inaam tumharey Rubb ki taraf se
  78,37,Us nihayat meharban khuda ki taraf se jo zameen aur aasmaano ka aur inke darmiyan ki har cheez ka malik hai jiske samney kisi ko bolne ka yara nahin
  78,38,Jis roz rooh aur malaika saff basta khade hongey. Koi na bolega siwaye uske jisey Rehman ijazat de aur jo theek baat kahey
  78,39,"Woh din bar-haqq hai, ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf palatne ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  78,40,"Humne tum logon ko us azaab se dara diya hai jo qareeb aa laga hai. Jis roz aadmi woh sab kuch dekh lega jo uske hathon ne aagey bheja hai, aur kafir pukar uthega ke kaash mai khaaq(mitti) hota"
  79,1,Kasam hai un (Farishton) ki jo doob kar khinchte hain
  79,2,aur aahistagi se (gently) nikaal le jataey hain
  79,3,Aur (un farishton ki jo qayinaat mein) tezi se tairtey phirtay hain
  79,4,phir (hukum baja laane mein) sabqat karte hain
  79,5,phir (ehkam-ilahi ke mutabiq) maamlaat ka intizam chalate hain
  79,6,Jis roz hila marey ga zalzalay ka jhatka
  79,7,Aur uske pichey ek aur jhatka padega
  79,8,Kuch dil hongey jo us roz khauf se kaanp rahey hongey
  79,9,Nigahein unki sehmi(downcast) hui hogi
  79,10,Yeh log kehte hain “Kya waqai hum palta kar phir wapas laaye jayenge?”
  79,11,“Kya jab hum khokli boseeda (hollow and rotten) haddiyan ban chuke hongey?”
  79,12,Kehne lagey “yeh wapsi to phir badey ghatey(nuksan) ki hogi”
  79,13,Halaanke yeh bas itna kaam hai ke ek zoar ki daant padegi
  79,14,Aur yakayk yeh khule maidan mein maujood hongey
  79,15,Kya tumhein Moosa ke qissey ki khabar pahunchi hai
  79,16,Jab uske Rubb ne usey Tuwa ke muqaddas wadi(valley) mein pukara tha
  79,17,"Ke Firaun ke paas ja, woh sarkash ho gaya hai"
  79,18,"Aur ussey keh, kya tu iske liye tayyar hai ke pakeezgi ikhtiyar karey"
  79,19,Aur mai terey Rubb ki taraf teri rehnumai karoon to (uska) khauf terey andar paida ho?”
  79,20,Phir Moosa ne (Firaun ke paas ja kar) usko badi nishani dikhai
  79,21,Magar usne jhutla diya aur na mana
  79,22,Phir chaal baaziyan karne ke liye palta
  79,23,Aur logon ko jama karke usne pukaar kar kaha
  79,24,“Main tumhara sabse bada Rubb hoon”
  79,25,Aakhir-e-kaar Allah ne usey aakhirat aur duniya ke azaab mei pakad liya
  79,26,Dar haqeeqat is mein badi ibrat hai har us shaks ke liye jo darey
  79,27,Kya tum logon ki takhleeq(paidaish) zyada sakht kaam hai ya aasmaan ki? Allah ne usko banaya
  79,28,Uski chhat(ceiling) khoob unchi uthayi phir uska tawazun qayam kiya(proportioned it)
  79,29,Aur uski raat dhaanki aur uska din nikala
  79,30,Iske baad zameen ko usne bichaya
  79,31,Uske andar se uska paani aur chara nikala
  79,32,Aur pahad usmein gaadh diye
  79,33,Saaman-e-zeist(provision) ke taur par tumharay liye aur tumharey maweshion ke liye
  79,34,Phir jab woh hungama-e-azeem barpa hoga
  79,35,Jis roz Insan apna sab kiya dhara yaad karega
  79,36,Aur har dekhne wale ke samney dozak khol kar rakh di jayegi
  79,37,To jisne sarkashi(transgress) ki thi
  79,38,Aur dunya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh di thi
  79,39,dozakh hi uska thikana hogi
  79,40,Aur jisne apne Rubb ke samney khade honay ka khauf kiya tha aur nafs ko buri khwaishaat se baaz rakha tha
  79,41,Jannat uska thikana hogi
  79,42,Yeh log tumse puchte hain ke aakhir woh ghadi kab aakar thehre gi
  79,43,Tumhara kya kaam ke us ka waqt batao
  79,44,Us ka ilm to Allah par khatm hai
  79,45,Tum sirf khabardar karne waley ho har us shaks ko jo uska khauff karey
  79,46,Jis roz yeh log usey dekh lengey to inhein yun mehsoos hoga ke (yeh duniya mein ya halat-e-mout mei) bas ek din ke pichle pehar ya aglay pehar tak thehrey hai
  80,1,"[The prophet] Tursh-rooh (frowned) hua aur berukhi barti"
  80,2,Is baat par ke woh andha us ke paas aa gaya
  80,3,"Tumhe kya khabar, shayad woh sudhar jaye"
  80,4,ya naseehat par dhyaan de aur naseeat karna us ke liye nafea(faiydamand) ho
  80,5,Jo shaks be-parwahi baratta hai
  80,6,Uski taraf to tum tawajjuh karte ho
  80,7,Halaanke agar wo na sudhrey to tum par uski kya zimmedari hai
  80,8,Aur jo khud tumharey paas dauda aata hai
  80,9,Aur woh darr raha hota hai
  80,10,Usse tum berukhi barat-tey ho
  80,11,Hargiz nahin yeh to ek naseehat hai
  80,12,jiska jee chahey isey qabool karey
  80,13,Yeh aisey saheefon mein darj hai jo mukarram hain
  80,14,"Buland martaba hain, pakeeza hain"
  80,15,muazzaz aur neik kaatibon ke
  80,16,haathon mein rehete hain
  80,17,Laanat ho Insan par kaisa sakht munkir-e-haq (denies the Truth) hai yeh
  80,18,Kis cheez se Allah ne isey paida kiya hai
  80,19,Nutfa ki ek boondh se Allah ne isey paida kiya phir iski taqdeer muqarrar ki
  80,20,Phir iske liye zindagi ki raah aasan ki
  80,21,Phir isey maut di aur qabr mei pahunchaya
  80,22,Phir jab chahey woh isey dobara utha khada karey
  80,23,"Hargiz nahi, isney woh farz ada nahi kiya jiska Allah ne isey hukum diya tha"
  80,24,Phir zara insaan apni khuraak(khane/food) ko dekhe
  80,25,Humne khoob paani lundhaya(poured)
  80,26,Phir zameen ko ajeeb tarah phada
  80,27,phir us ke andar ugaye galley(grain)
  80,28,Aur angoor aur tarkariyan
  80,29,Aur zaitoon aur khajoorein
  80,30,Aur ghaney baagh(orchards)
  80,31,Aur tarah tarah ke phal aur chaarey
  80,32,Tumharey liye aur tumharey maweshion(cattles) ke liye saman-e-zeist(provision )ke taur par
  80,33,Aakhir-e-kaar jab woh kaan behrey kar deney wali aawaz buland hogi
  80,34,Us roz aadmi apne bhai
  80,35,Aur apni maa aur apne baap
  80,36,Aur apni biwi aur apni aulad se bhagega
  80,37,Unmein har shaks par us din aisa waqt aa padega ke usay apne siwa kisi ka hosh na hoga
  80,38,Kuch chehrey us roz damak rahe hongey
  80,39,Hashash bashash aur khush o khurram hongey
  80,40,Aur kuch chehron par uss roz khaak(dust) udd rahi hogi
  80,41,Aur kalons(darkness) chayi hui hogi
  80,42,Yahi kafir o fajir (unbelivers and wicked) log hain
  81,1,Jab Suraj lapeit diya jayega
  81,2,Aur jab taarey bikhar jayenge
  81,3,Aur jab pahad chalaye jayenge
  81,4,Aur jab dus mahine ki hamila ountniyan (she-camels) apne haal par chod di jayengi
  81,5,Aur jab jungli jaanwar sameth kar ikhattey kar diye jayenge
  81,6,Aur jab samandar bhadka diye jayenge
  81,7,Aur jab jaane (Jismon se) jodh di jayengi
  81,8,Aur jab zinda gaadi hui(buried) ladki se pucha jayega
  81,9,ke woh kis kasoor mei mari gayi
  81,10,Aur jab aamal-naame(scrolls of deeds) kholey jayenge
  81,11,Aur jab aasman ka purda hata diya jayega
  81,12,Aur jab Jahannam dehkayi jayegi
  81,13,Aur jab Jannat qareeb le aayi jayegi
  81,14,Us waqt har shaks ko maloom ho jayega ke woh kya lekar aaya hai
  81,15,Pas nahin main kasam khata hoon
  81,16,Palatne aur chup janey wale taaron ki
  81,17,Aur Raat ki jabke woh ruksat hui
  81,18,Aur subah ki jabke usne saans liya
  81,19,Yeh fil waqea ek buzurg paigam-bar ka qaul(word) hai
  81,20,"Jo badi tawanai (might) rakhta hai, Arsh waley ke yahan buland martaba hai"
  81,21,"Wahan uska hukum mana jata hai, Woh ba-aitamad (trustworthy) hai"
  81,22,Aur (aey ehle Makkah) tumhara rafeeq(companion) majnoon(mad) nahin hai
  81,23,Usne us paigambar ko roshan ufaq (clear horizon) par dekha hai
  81,24,Aur woh gaib (ke is ilam ko logon tak pahunchane) ke maamle mei bakheel nahin hai
  81,25,Aur yeh kisi shaitan-e-mardood ka qaul nahin hai
  81,26,Phir tum log kidhar chaley ja rahey ho
  81,27,Yeh to saarey jahan walon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  81,28,Tum mein se har us shaks ke liye jo raah-e-raast par chalna chahta ho
  81,29,Aur tumharey chahney se kuch nahin hota jab tak Allah Rabb-ul-Aalameen na chahey
  82,1,Jab Aasman phat jayega
  82,2,Aur jab taarey bikhar jayengey
  82,3,Aur jab samandar phaad diye jayengey
  82,4,Aur jab qabrein khol di jayengi
  82,5,Us waqt har shaks ko uska agla pichla sab kiya dhara maloom ho jayega
  82,6,Aey insaan kis cheez ne tujhey apne uss Rubb-e-kareem ki taraf se dhoke mein daal diya
  82,7,"Jisne tujhey paida kiya, tujhey nek-suk se durust kiya(shaped you), tujhe mutanasib(well-proportioned) banaya"
  82,8,Aur jis surat mein chaha tujhko jodh kar tayyar kiya
  82,9,Hargiz nahin balke (asal baat yeh hai ke) tumlog jaza-o-saza ko jhutlate ho
  82,10,Halaanke tumpar nigraan muqarrar hain
  82,11,Aisey muazzaz kaatib
  82,12,Jo tumharey har fail(amal) ko jantey hain
  82,13,Yaqeenan neik log mazey mei hongey
  82,14,Aur beshak badkar log jahannam me jayenge
  82,15,Jaza ke din woh is mein daakhil hongey
  82,16,Aur us se hargiz gayab na ho sakengey
  82,17,Aur tum kya jaante ho ke woh jaza ka din kya hai
  82,18,Haan tumhein kya khabar ke woh jaza ka din kya hai
  82,19,"Yeh woh din hai jab kisi shaks ke liye kuch karna kisi ke bas mei na hoga, faisla us din bilkul Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hoga"
  83,1,Tabahi hai dandi maarne walon ke liye
  83,2,Jinka haal yeh hai ke jab logon se letey hai to pura pura letey hai
  83,3,Aur jab unko naap kar ya toal kar dete hai to unhein ghata dete hai
  83,4,Kya yeh log nahin samajhte ke ek badey din
  83,5,Yeh utha kar laaye jaaney waley hain
  83,6,Uss din jabke sab log Rabb-ul-Aalamin ke samney khadey hongey
  83,7,"Hargiz nahin, yaqeenan badkaaron ka naam-e- aamal qaid-khane ke daftar mei hai"
  83,8,Aur tumhey kya maloom ke woh qaid-khaney ka daftar kya hai
  83,9,Ek kitaab hai likhi hui
  83,10,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlane walon ke liye
  83,11,Jo roz-e-jaza ko jhutlatay hain
  83,12,Aur usey nahin jhutlata magar har woh shaks jo hadd se guzar janey wala bad-amal hai
  83,13,Usey jab hamari ayaat sunayi jaati hain to kehta hai yeh to agley waqton ki kahaniyan hai
  83,14,"Hargiz nahin, balke darasal in logon ke dilon par inke burey aamal ka zang(rust) chadh gaya hai"
  83,15,Hargiz nahin bil yaqeen us roz yeh apne Rubb ki deed(deedar) se mehroom rakhey jayenge
  83,16,Phir yeh jahannum mein jaa padenge
  83,17,Phir insey kaha jayega ke yeh wahi cheez hai jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay
  83,18,"Hargiz nahin, beshak neik aadmion ka naam-e-aamal buland paya logon ke daftar mein hai"
  83,19,Aur tumhein kya khabar ke kya hai woh buland paya logon ka daftar
  83,20,Ek likhi hui kitaab hai
  83,21,Jiski nigeh-daasht muqarrab farishtay karte hain
  83,22,Beshak neik log badey mazey mein hongey
  83,23,Unchi masnadon(couches) par baithay nazarey kar rahey hongey
  83,24,Unke chehron par tum khushhaali ki raunak mehsoos karogey
  83,25,Unko nafees tareen sarband sharaab pilayi jayegi jispar mushk ki mohar(seal) lagi hogi
  83,26,Jo log dusron par baazi le jana chahtey hon woh is cheez ko haasil karne mei baazi le jane ki koshish karein
  83,27,Us sharaab mei tasneem ki aamezish(mixture) hogi
  83,28,Yeh ek chasma hai jiske paani ke saath muqarrab log sharaab piyengey
  83,29,Mujrim log duniya mein imaan laane walon ka mazaak udate thay
  83,30,Jab unke paas se guzarte to aankhein maar maar kar unki taraf isharey karte thay
  83,31,Apne gharon ki taraf palat-tey to mazey letey huey palat-tey thay
  83,32,Aur jab unhein dekhte to kehte thay ke yeh behke huey log hain
  83,33,Halaanke woh un par nigran banakar nahin bhejey gaye thay
  83,34,Aaj imaan laane waley kuffar par hans rahay hai
  83,35,Masnadon par baithey huey unka haal dekh rahey hain
  83,36,Mil gaya na kafiron ko un harkaton ka sawab jo woh kiya karte thay
  84,1,Jab aasman phatt jayega
  84,2,Aur apne Rubb kay famaan ki tameel karega aur uske liye haq yahi hai (ke apne Rubb ka hukum maney)
  84,3,Aur jab zameen phaila di jayegi
  84,4,Aur jo kuch uske andar hai usey bahar phenk kar khaali ho jayegi
  84,5,Aur apne Rubb ke hukum ki tameel karegi aur uske liye haq yahi hai (kay uski tameel karey)
  84,6,Aey insaan tu kashaan kashaan apne Rubb ki taraf chala ja raha hai(striving unto your Lord) aur ussey milney wala hai
  84,7,Phir jiska naam-e-aamal uske seedhey haath mei diya gaya
  84,8,Ussey halka hisaab liya jayega
  84,9,Aur woh apne logon ki taraf khush khush paltega
  84,10,Raha woh shaks jiska naam-e-aamal us ki peeth ke pichey diya jayega
  84,11,To woh maut ko pukarega
  84,12,Aur bhadakti hui aag mei ja padega
  84,13,Woh apne ghar walon mein magan tha
  84,14,Usne samjha tha ke usey kabhi palatna nahin hai
  84,15,"Palatna kaise na tha, uska Rubb uske kartoot dekh raha tha"
  84,16,Pas nahin mai kasam khata hon shafaq(twilight) ki
  84,17,Aur raat ki aur jo kuch woh sameith leti hai
  84,18,Aur chaand ki jabke woh maah-e-kaamil (full) ho jata hai
  84,19,Tumko zaroor darja ba darja ek haalat se dusri halat ki taraf guzarte chalay jana hai
  84,20,Phir in logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh imaan nahin laatey
  84,21,Aur jab Quran inke samney pada jata hai to sajda nahin karte
  84,22,Balke yeh munkireen to ulta jhutlatay hain
  84,23,Halaanke jo kuch yeh (apne naam-e-aamal mein) jama kar rahey hain Allah usey khoob janta hai
  84,24,Lihaza inko dardnaak azaab ki basharat dedo
  84,25,Albatta jo log imaan le aaye hain aur jinho ne neik aamal kiye hain unke liye kabhi khatam na honay wala ajar hai
  85,1,Kasam hai mazboot qalon waley (impregnable castles )aasman ki
  85,2,Aur us din ki jiska wada kiya gaya hai
  85,3,Aur dekhnay walay ki aur dekhi janey wali cheez ki
  85,4,kay maarey gaye gaddey(pit) waley
  85,5,"uss gaddey(pit) waley] jis mei khoob bhadakte huey indhan ki aag thi"
  85,6,jabke woh us gaddey ke kinare par baithay huey thay
  85,7,Aur jo kuch woh imaan laney walon ke saath kar rahey thay usey dekh rahey thay
  85,8,Aur un ehley imaan se unki dushmani iske siwa kisi wajah se na thi ke woh us khuda par imaan le aaye thay jo zabardast aur apni zaat mei aap mahmood(praiseworthy) hai
  85,9,"Jo aasmano aur zameen ki sultanat ka maalik hai, aur woh khuda sab kuch dekh raha hai"
  85,10,"Jin logon ne momin mardon aur auraton par zulm o sitam toda aur phir ussey taib na huey, yaqeenan unke liye jahannum ka azaab hai aur unke liye jalaye janey ki saza hai"
  85,11,"Jo log imaan laaye aur jinho ne neik amal kiye yaqeenan unke liye jannat ke baagh hain jinke nichey nehrein behti hongi, yeh hai badi kamyabi"
  85,12,Dar haqeeqat tumharey Rubb ki pakad badi sakht hai
  85,13,Wahi pehli baar paida karta hai aur wahi dobara paida karega
  85,14,"Aur woh bakshne wala hai, mohabbat karne wala hai"
  85,15,"Arsh ka maalik hai, buzurg-o-bartar hai"
  85,16,Aur jo kuch chahey kar daalney wala hai
  85,17,Kya tumhey lashkaron ki khabar pahunchi hai
  85,18,Firoun aur samood (ke lashkaron) ki
  85,19,Magar jinho ne kufr kiya hai woh jhutlaney mein lagey huey hain
  85,20,Halaanke Allah ne unko gherey mein le rakha hai
  85,21,(unke jhutlaney se iss quran ka kuch nahin bigadta) balkey yeh quran buland paya hai
  85,22,Us loah mei (naqsh hai) jo mehfooz hai
  86,1,Kasam hai aasmaan ki aur raat ko namudaar honay wale ki
  86,2,Aur tum kya jaano kay woh raat ko namudaar honay wala kya hai
  86,3,Chamakta hua tara
  86,4,koi jaan aisi nahin hai jiske upar koi nigehbaan na ho
  86,5,Phir zara Insan yahi dekh le ke woh kis cheez se paida kiya gaya hai
  86,6,Ek uchalne wale pani se paida kiya gaya hai
  86,7,Jo peet aur seeney ki haddiyon kay darmiyan se nikalta hai
  86,8,Yaqeenan woh (khaliq) usey dobara paida karne par qadir hai
  86,9,Jis roz poshida asraar ki jaanch padtal hogi
  86,10,Us waqt Insan ke paas na khud apna koi zoar hoga aur na koi uski madad karne wala hoga
  86,11,Kasam hai baarish barsane waley aasman ki
  86,12,Aur (nabataat ugte waqt) phatt jane wali zameen ki
  86,13,Yeh ek jachi-tuli baat hai
  86,14,Hasi mazak nahin hai
  86,15,yeh log kuch chalein chal rahe hain
  86,16,Aur mai bhi ek chaal chal raha hoon
  86,17,"Pas chodh do aey nabi, in kafiron ko ek zara ki zara in ke haal par chod do"
  87,1,(Aey nabi) Apne Rubb-e-bartar kay naam ki tasbeeh karo
  87,2,Jisne paida kiya aur tanasub qayam kiya (then proportioned it)
  87,3,Jisne taqdeer banayi phir raah dikhayi
  87,4,Jisne nabataat(pasture) ugayi
  87,5,Phir unko siyah kuda karkat bana diya
  87,6,Hum tumhey padhwa dengey phir tum nahin bhuloge
  87,7,Siwaye uske jo Allah chahey.Woh zahir ko bhi jaanta hai aur jo kuch posheeda(hidden) hai usko bhi
  87,8,Aur hum tumhein aasaan tarikey ki sahoolat dete hain
  87,9,lihaza tum naseehat karo agar naseehat nafey(faiydamand) ho
  87,10,Jo shaks darta hai wo naseehat qabool karlega
  87,11,Aur ussey guraiz karega woh intehayi bad-bakht
  87,12,Jo badi aag mei jayega
  87,13,phir na usmein marega aur na jiyega
  87,14,Falah paa gaya woh jisne pakizgi ikhtiyar ki
  87,15,Aur apne Rubb ka naam yaad kiya phir namaz padhi
  87,16,Magar tumlog duniya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh detay ho
  87,17,halaanke aakhirat behtar hai aur baqi rehne wali hai
  87,18,Yahi baat pehle aaey huey saheefon(scriptures) mei bhi kahi gayi thi
  87,19,Ibrahim aur Moosa ke saheefon mein
  88,1,Kya tumhein us chaa janey wali aafat ki khabar pahunchi hai
  88,2,Kuch chehrey us roz khauff zada hongey
  88,3,Sakht mashakkat kar rahe hongey
  88,4,"Thakey jatey hongey, shadeed aag mei jhulas rahe hongey"
  88,5,khaultey(boiling) huey chashmey(spring) ka paani unhei peene ko diya jaeyga
  88,6,khar-dar(kaante-daar) sukhi ghaans ke siwa koi khana unke liye na hoga
  88,7,Jo na mota karey na bhook mitaye
  88,8,kuch chehrey us roz ba-raunak hongey
  88,9,Apne kar-guzari par khush hongey
  88,10,Aali muqaam jannat mein hongey
  88,11,koi behuda baat wahan na sunengey
  88,12,Usmein chasmey rawan hongey
  88,13,Uske andar unchi masnadein hongi
  88,14,Sagar rakhey huey hongey
  88,15,gaon takiyon(cushions arrayed) ke qatarein lagi hongi
  88,16,Aur nafees farsh bichey huey hongey
  88,17,(yeh log nahin mantey) to kya yeh unton ko nahin dekhtey ke kaisey banaye gaye
  88,18,Asman ko nahin dekhte ke kaise uthaya gaya
  88,19,Pahadon ko nahin dekhtey ke kaisey jamaye gaye
  88,20,Aur zameen ko nahin dekhtey ke kaisey bichayi gayi
  88,21,"Acha to ( aey nabi) nasihat kiye jao, tum bas nasihat hi karne wale ho"
  88,22,kuch inpar jabr karne wale nahin ho
  88,23,Albatta jo shaks mooh modega aur inkar karega
  88,24,To Allah usko bhaari saza dega
  88,25,In logon ko palatna hamari taraf hi hai
  88,26,Phir inka hisab lena hamare hi zimmey hai
  89,1,Kasam hai fajr ki
  89,2,Aur dus raaton ki
  89,3,Aur jufft(even) aur taaq(odd) ki
  89,4,Aur Raat ki jabke woh ruksat ho rahi ho
  89,5,kya ismein kisi sahib-e-aqal ke liye koi kasam hai
  89,6,Tumne dekha nahin ke tumhare Rubb ne kya bartao kiya
  89,7,Unchey sutuno waley Aad-e-iram kay saath
  89,8,Jinke manind koi qaum duniya kay mulkon mein paida nahin ki gayi thi
  89,9,Aur Samood ke saath jinhon ne wadi mei chattane tarashi thi
  89,10,Aur mekhon waley Firoun kay saath
  89,11,Yeh woh log (thay) jinhone duniya kay mulkon mein badi sarkashi ki thi
  89,12,Aur inmein bahut fasaad failaya tha
  89,13,Aakhir-e-kaar tumhare Rubb ne inpar azaab ka koda barsa diya
  89,14,Haqeeqat yeh hai kay tumhara Rubb ghaath(watchful) lagaye huey hai
  89,15,Magar Insan ka haal yeh hai kay uska Rubb jab usko aazmaish mein daalta hai aur usey izzat aur niyamat deta hai to woh kehta hai kay mere Rubb ne mujhey izzatdar bana diya
  89,16,Aur jab woh usko azmaish mein daalta hai aur uska rizq uspar tangg kar deta hai to woh kehta hai mere Rubb ne mujhey zaleel kar diya
  89,17,"Hargiz nahin, balke tum yateem se izzat ka sulook nahin kartey"
  89,18,Aur miskeen ko khana khilane par ek dusrey ko nahin uksatey
  89,19,Aur Miras(inheritance) ka sara maal sameith kar kha jatey ho
  89,20,Aur maal ki muhabbat mei buri tarah giraftar ho
  89,21,Hargiz nahin jab zameen pai dar pai qoot qoot kar regzaar bana di jayegi
  89,22,Aur tumahra Rubb jalwa farma hoga is haal mei kay farishtey saff dar saff khade hongey
  89,23,"Aur jahannum us roz samnay le aayi jaeygi, us din Insan ko samajh ayegi aur us waqt us ke samajhne ka kya hasil"
  89,24,Woh kahega ke kaash maine apni is zindagi ke liye kuch peshgi saman kiya hota
  89,25,Phir us din Allah jo azaab dega waisa azaab dene wala koi nahin
  89,26,Aur Allah jaisa bandhega waisa bandhne wala koi nahin
  89,27,(Dusri taraf irshad hoga) Aey nafsey mutmain(reassured soul/pious)
  89,28,Chal apne Rubb ki taraf is haal mein ke tu (apne anjam-e-neik se) khush (Aur apne Rubb kay nazdeek) pasandida hai
  89,29,Shamil ho ja mere (neik) bandon mein
  89,30,Aur dakhil hoja meri jannat mein
  90,1,Nahin mai kasam khata hoon is shehar(city) ki
  90,2,Aur haal yeh hai ke (Aey nabi) is shehar mein tumko halal kar liya gaya hai
  90,3,Aur kasam khata hoon baap(Adam) ki aur us aulad ki jo ussey paida hui
  90,4,Dar haqeeqat humne Insan ko mushakkat mein paida kiya hai
  90,5,Kya usne yeh samajh rakhha hai kay uspar koi qaabu na paa sakega
  90,6,Kehta hai ke maine dhairon maal udaa diya
  90,7,Kya woh samajhta hai kay kisi ne usko nahin dekha
  90,8,Kya humne usey do aankhein
  90,9,Aur ek zubaan aur do honth nahin diye
  90,10,Aur dono numayan raste usey (nahin) dikha diye
  90,11,Magar usne dushwar guzar ghati(steep) se guzarne ki himmat na ki
  90,12,Aur tum kya jaano kay kya hai woh dushwar guzar ghaati
  90,13,Kisi gardan ko gulami se chudana
  90,14,Ya faake ke din
  90,15,kisi qareebi yateem
  90,16,Ya khaak nasheen miskeen ko khana khilana
  90,17,Phir (iske saath yeh kay) aadmi un logon mein shamil ho jo imaan laye aur jinhon ne ek dusrey ko sabr aur (khalq-e-khuda par) raham ki talqeen ki
  90,18,Yeh log hain dayein baazu(right hand) waley
  90,19,Aur jinhon ne hamari aayat ko mann-ney se inkar kiya woh bayen bazu(left hand) waley hain
  90,20,Un par aag chaayi hui hogi
  91,1,Suraj aur uski dhoop ki kasam
  91,2,Aur Chand ki kasam jabke wo uske pichey aata hai
  91,3,Aur din ki kasam jabke woh (Suraj ko) numaya kar deta hai
  91,4,Aur raat ki kasam jabke woh (suraj ko) dhank leti hai
  91,5,Aur aasman ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey qayam kiya
  91,6,Aur zameen ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey bichaya
  91,7,Aur nafs-e-Insani ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey hamwar kiya
  91,8,Phir uski badi aur uski parhezgari uss par ilham kar di
  91,9,Yaqeenan falah pa gaya woh jisne nafs ka tazkiya kiya
  91,10,Aur na-murad hua woh jisne usko daba diya
  91,11,Samood ne apni sarkashi ki bina par jhutlaya
  91,12,Jab us qaum ka sab se zyada shaqi (Badnaseeb) aadmi biphar kar utha
  91,13,To Allah ke Rasool ne un logon se kaha ke khabardar Allah ki ountni (she-camel) ko (haath na lagana) aur uske paani peene (mein maane na hona)
  91,14,Magar unhon ne uski baat ko jhuta qarar diya aur ountni ko maar dala. Aakhir-e-kaar unke gunah ke padash mein unke Rubb ne unpar aisi aafat toodi ke ek saath sab ko paywand-e-khaaq kar diya
  91,15,Aur usey (apne is fail kay) kisi burey natije ka koi khauf(darr) nahin hai
  92,1,Kasam hai raat ki jabke woh chaa jaaye
  92,2,Aur din ki jabke woh roshan ho
  92,3,Aur us zaat ki jisne nar(male) aur maada(female) ko paida kiya
  92,4,Dar haqeeqat tum logon ki koshishein mukhtalif qism ki hai
  92,5,To jisne (rah e khuda mein) maal diya aur (khuda ki nafarmani se) parhez kiya
  92,6,Aur bhalayi ko sach mana
  92,7,Usko hum aasan raastey kay liye sahulat denge
  92,8,Aur jisne bukhl(kanjoosi) kiya aur (apney khuda se) be niyazi(self-sufficient/independent) barti
  92,9,aur bhalayi ko jhutlaya
  92,10,Usko hum sakht rastey kay liye sahulat dengey
  92,11,Aur uska maal aakhir uske kis kaam aayega jabke woh halaq ho jaye
  92,12,Beshak rasta batana hamare zimmey hai
  92,13,aur dar haqeeqat aakhirat aur duniya dono kay hum hi malik hai
  92,14,Pas maine tumko khabardar kar diya hai bhadakti hui aag se
  92,15,Usmein nahin jhulsega magar woh intihayi badbakth
  92,16,jisne jhutlaya aur mooh phera
  92,17,Aur usse door rakkha jayega woh nihayat parhezgaar
  92,18,Jo paakiza honay ki khatir apna maal deta hai
  92,19,Uspar kisi ka koi ehsan nahin hai jiska badla usey dena ho
  92,20,Woh to sirf apne Rubb-e-bartrar ki raza joii ke liye yeh kaam karta hai
  92,21,Aur zaroor woh (us se) khush hoga
  93,1,Kasam hai rozey roshan ki
  93,2,Aur raat ki jabke woh sukoon ke saath taari ho jaye
  93,3,(Aey nabi) tumharey Rubb ne tumko hargiz nahin chodha aur na woh naraaz hua
  93,4,Aur yaqeenan tumhare liya baad ka daur pehle daur se behtar hai
  93,5,Aur anqareeb tumhra Rubb tumko itna dega ke tum khush ho jaogey
  93,6,Kya usne tumko yateem nahin paya aur phir thikana faraham kiya
  93,7,Aur tumhey nawaqif-e-raah paya aur phir hidayat bakshi
  93,8,Aur tumhein nadaar(in want) paya aur phir maldar kar diya
  93,9,Lihaza yateem par sakhti na karo
  93,10,Aur saayil(maangne waley) ko na jhidko
  93,11,Aur apne Rubb ki niyamt ka izhar karo
  94,1,(Aey Nabi) kya humne tumhara seena tumhare liye khol nahin diya
  94,2,Aur tumpar se woh bhari bojh utar diya
  94,3,Jo tumhari qamar todhe daal raha tha
  94,4,Aur tumhare khatir tumharey zikr ka awazah buland kar diya
  94,5,Pas haqeeqat yeh hai kay tangi kay saat farakhi bhi hai
  94,6,Beshak tangi kay saath farakhi bhi hai
  94,7,Lihaza jab tum faarig ho to Ibadat ki mushakkat mei lag jao
  94,8,Aur apne Rubb ki taraf raagib ho
  95,1,Kasam hai Injir(fig) ki aur Zaitun ki
  95,2,Aur Tur-e-sina (Mount Sinai)
  95,3,Aur is pur-aman shehar (Makkah) ki
  95,4,Humne Insan ko behtarin saakht par paida kiya
  95,5,Phir usey ulta pher kar humne sab neechon se neech kar diya
  95,6,Siwaye un logon ke jo iman laye aur neik amal karte rahey kay unke liye kabhi khatam na hone wala ajar hai
  95,7,Pas (aey nabi) iske baad kaun jaza o saza ke maamle mei tumko jhutla sakta hai
  95,8,Kya Allah sab hakimon se bada hakim nahin hai
  96,1,Padho (Aey Nabi) apne Rubb ke naam ke saath Jisne paida kiya
  96,2,Jamey huey khoon ke ek lothdey se Insan ki takhliq ki
  96,3,Padho aur tumhara Rubb bada kareem hai
  96,4,jisne qalam ke zariya se ilm sikhaya
  96,5,Insan ko woh ilm diya jisey woh na jaanta tha
  96,6,"Hargiz nahin, Insan sarkahshi karta hai"
  96,7,Is bina par ke woh apne aap ko be niyaz dekhta hai
  96,8,(halaanke) palatna yaqeenan tere Rubb hi ki taraf hai
  96,9,Tumne dekha us shaks ko
  96,10,Jo ek banday ko mana karta hai jabke woh namaz padta ho
  96,11,Tumhara kya khayal hai agar (woh banda) raah e raast par ho
  96,12,ya parhezgari ki talqeen karta ho
  96,13,Tumhara kya khayal hai agar (yeh mana karne wala shakhs haqq ko) jhutlata aur mooh moadta ho
  96,14,Kya woh nahin jaanta ke Allah dekh raha hai
  96,15,Hargiz nahin agar woh baaz na aaya to hum uski peshani ke baal pakad kar usey khinchey ge
  96,16,Us peshani ko jo jhooti aur sakth khatakaar hai
  96,17,Woh bulaley apne haamiyon ki toli ko
  96,18,Hum bhi azaab ke farishton ko bula lengey
  96,19,"Hargiz nahin, uski baat na mano aur sajda karo aur (apne Rubb ka) qurb hasil karo"
  97,1,Humne is (Quran) ko shab-e-qadr mei nazil kiya hai
  97,2,Aur tum kya jano kay shab-e-qadr kya hai
  97,3,Shab-e-qadr hazar mahino se zyada behtar hai
  97,4,Farishtey aur rooh(Jibrael) us mein apne Rubb ke izn(permission) se har hukm le kar utarte hai
  97,5,Woh raat sarasar salamati hai tulu e fajr tak
  98,1,Ehle kitab aur Mushrikin mein se jo log kafir thay (woh apne kufr se) baaz aane walay na thay jab tak ke unke paas dalil e roshan na aa jaye
  98,2,(Yani) Allah ke taraf se ek Rasool jo paak sahife padh kar sunaye
  98,3,Jin mein bilkul raast aur durust tehrirein likhi hui ho
  98,4,Pehle jin logon ko kitab di gayi thi unmei tafarqa barpa(split/divide) nahin hua magar is ke baad ke un ke paas (raahe rast ka) bayan e wazeh aa chuka tha
  98,5,"Aur unko iske siwa koi hukum nahin diya gaya tha ke Allah ke bandagi karein apne deen ko uske liye khalis karke. Bilkul yaksu ho kar, Aur namaz qayam karein aur zakat de yahi nihayat sahih-o-durust deen hai"
  98,6,"Ehle kitaab aur mushrikin mein se jin logon ne kufr kiya hai woh yaqeenan jahannam ki aag mein jayenge aur hamesha us mein rahenge, yeh log badh-tareen e khalayek(creation) hain"
  98,7,Jo log iman le aaye aur jinhon nay neik amal kiye woh yaqeenan behtareen-e-khalayeq hai
  98,8,Unki jaza unke Rubb ke yahan dayimi(eternal) qayam ki jannatein hain jinke nichey nehrein beh rahi hongi. Woh unmein hamesha hamesh rahenge. Allah unse razi hua aur woh Allah se razi huey. Yeh kuch hai us shaks ke liye jisne apne Rubb ka khauf kiya ho
  99,1,Jab zameen apni puri shiddat kay saath hila daali jayegi
  99,2,Aur zameen apne andar kay sarey bojh nikal kar bahar daal degi
  99,3,Aur Insan kahega ke yeh isko kya ho raha hai
  99,4,Us roz woh apne (upar guzre huey) halaat bayan karegi
  99,5,Kyunke tere Rubb ne usey (aisa karne ka) hukm diya hoga
  99,6,Us roz log mutafarrik halat mein paltenge taakay unke aamal unko dikhaey jayein
  99,7,Phir jisne zarra barabar neki ki hogi woh usko dekh lega
  99,8,Aur jisne zarra barabar badi ki hogi woh usko dekh lega
  100,1,Kasam hai un (ghodon) ki jo phunkare marte hue dhaudte hai
  100,2,Phir (apne tapon se) chingariyan jhaadte hain
  100,3,Phir subah sawere chapa marte hain
  100,4,Phir is mauke par gard o gubar udatey hai
  100,5,Phir isi halat mei kisi majmey ke andar ja ghustey hai
  100,6,Haqiqat yeh hai ke Insan apne Rubb ka bada nashukra hai
  100,7,Aur woh khud is par gawah hai
  100,8,Aur woh maal-o-daulat ki muhabbat mei buri tarah mubtala hai
  100,9,To kya woh us waqt ko nahin janta jab qabron mein jo kuch (madfun) hai usey nikal liya jayega
  100,10,Aur seeno mein jo kuch (makhfi) hai usey baramad karke uski jaanch padtal ki jayegi
  100,11,Yaqeenan unka Rubb us roz unse khoob bakhabar hoga
  101,1,Azeem hadisa
  101,2,Kya hai woh azeem hadisa
  101,3,Tum kya jano ke woh azeem hadisa kya hai
  101,4,woh din jab log bhikre huey parwano ki tarah
  101,5,Aur pahad rang bi rangi dhunki hui oon ke tarah hongey
  101,6,Phir jiske palade bhari hongey
  101,7,Woh dil pasand aish mei hoga
  101,8,Aur jis kay palade halke hongey
  101,9,Uski jaye qarar gehri khayi hogi
  101,10,Aur tumhein kya khabar kay woh kya cheez hai
  101,11,Bhadakti hui Aag
  102,1,Tum logon ko zyada se zyada aur ek dusre se badh kar duniya hasil karne ki dhun ne gaflat mei daal rakha hai
  102,2,Yahan tak ke (isi fikr mei) tum lab-e-gaur tak pahunch jatey ho
  102,3,"Hargiz nahin, ankareeb tumko maloom ho jayega"
  102,4,"phir (sunlo kay) hargiz nahin, ankarib tumko maloom ho jayega"
  102,5,Hargiz nahin agar tum yaqeeni ilm ki haisiyat se (is rawish ke anjam ko) jantey hotey (to tumhara yeh tarze amal na hota)
  102,6,Tum dozakh dekh kar rahogey
  102,7,Phir (sun lo ke) tum bilkul yaqeen kay saath usey dekh logey
  102,8,Phir zaroor us roz tum se in neyamaton kay barey mein jawab talabi ki jayegi
  103,1,Zamane ki qasam
  103,2,Insan dar haqeeqat badey khasarey(nuksaan) mein hai
  103,3,Siwaye un logon ke jo iman laye aur neik aamal karte rahe aur ek dusrey ko haqq ki nasihat aur sabr ki talqeen karte rahe
  104,1,Tabahi hai har us shaks ke liye jo (moonh dar moonh) logon par taan aur (peeth peechey) buraiyan karne ka khugar hai
  104,2,Jisne maal jama kiya aur usey gin gin kar rakkha
  104,3,Woh samajhta hai ke us ka maal hamesha uske paas rahega
  104,4,"Hargiz nahin, woh shaks to chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah mein phenk diya jayega"
  104,5,Aur tum kya jano ke kya hai woh chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah
  104,6,Allah ki aag khoob bhadkayi hui
  104,7,Jo dilon tak pahunchey gi
  104,8,Woh un par dhaank kar bandh kar di jayegi
  104,9,(Is halat mei ke woh) unchey unchey sutuno mei (ghirey huey hongey)
  105,1,Tumne dekha nahin ke tumhare Rubb ne haathi walon ke saath kya kiya
  105,2,Kya usne unki tadbir ko akarat nahin kar diya
  105,3,Aur un par parindo ke jhund ke jhund bhej diye
  105,4,Jo un par pakey huey mitti ke patthar phenk rahey thay
  105,5,Phir un ka yeh haal kar diya jaise janwaron ka khaya hua bhoosa
  106,1,Chunke Quresh manoos huey
  106,2,(yani) Jaadey(winter) aur garmi ke safaron se manoos
  106,3,Lihaza un ko chahiye ke is ghar ke Rubb ki ibadat karein
  106,4,Jisne unhein bhook se bacha kar khane ko diya aur khauf se bacha kar aman ata kiya
  107,1,Tum ne dekha us shaks ko jo aakhirat ki jaza va saza ko jhutlata hai
  107,2,Wahi to hai jo yateem ko dhakkey deta hai
  107,3,Aur miskeen ka khana dene par nahin uksata
  107,4,Phir tabahi hai un namaz padhne walon ke liye
  107,5,Jo apni namaz se gaflat barat-tey hain
  107,6,Jo riya-kaari(dikhawa) karte hai
  107,7,Aur maamuli zarurat ki cheezen (logon ko) dene se gurez karte hai
  108,1,(Aey Nabi ) Hum ne tumhein kausar ata kar diya
  108,2,Pas tum apne Rubb hi ke liye namaz padho aur qurbani karo
  108,3,Tumhara dushman hi jadh-kata hai
  109,1,Kehdo ke aey kafiron
  109,2,Main unki ibadat nahin karta jinki ibadat tum karte ho
  109,3,Aur na tum uski ibadat karne wale ho jiski ibadat mai karta hoon
  109,4,Aur na mai unki ibadat karne wala hoon jinki ibadat tum ne ki hai
  109,5,Aur na tum uski ibadat karne waley ho jiski ibadat main karta hoon
  109,6,Tumhare liye tumhara deen hai aur mere liye mera deen
  110,1,Jab Allah ki madad aa jaye aur fatah naseeb ho jaye
  110,2,Aur (aey Nabi s.a.s) tum dekh lo ke log fauj dar fauj Allah ke deen mein dakhil ho rahey hain
  110,3,To apne Rubb ki hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo Aur us se magfirat ki duaa maango. Beshak woh bada tauba qabool karne wala hai
  111,1,Toot gaye Abu Lahab ke haath aur na-murad ho gaya woh
  111,2,Uska maal aur jo kuch us ne kamaya woh uske kisi kaam na aaya
  111,3,Zaroor woh shola zan Aag mei dala jayega
  111,4,Aur (us ke saath) us ki joru(wife) bhi lagai bujhai karne wali
  111,5,Us ki gardan(neck) mein moonj ki rassi hogi
  112,1,"Kaho woh Allah hai, Yakta"
  112,2,Allah sab se bay-niyaz hai aur sab us kay mohtaj hain
  112,3,Na uski koi aulad hai aur na woh kisi ki aulad
  112,4,Aur koi uska humsar nahin hai
  113,1,Kaho main panaah maangta hoon subah ke Rubb ki
  113,2,Har us cheez ke shar se jo usne paida ki hai
  113,3,Aur raat ki tareeki ke sharr se jab ke woh chaa jaye
  113,4,Aur girhon mein phoonkne walon (ya waliyon) ke sharr se
  113,5,Aur hasid(envies) ke sharr se jab ke woh hasad(envy) karey
  114,1,"Kaho, main panah maangta hoon insano ke Rubb"
  114,2,Insano ke badshah
  114,3,Insano ke hakiki maabood ki
  114,4,us waswasa dalne wale ke shar se jo baar baar palat kar aata hai
  114,5,Jo logon ke dilon mei waswasey daalta hai
  114,6,khwah woh jinno mein se ho ya Insano mein se